# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:15
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_21a82833:

    # "My alarm's beeping shatters the early morning quiet, and I find myself wondering where to find the motivation to rise."
    "鬧鐘的聲音打破了清晨的寧靜，睡眼朦朧的我仍未能找到起床的動力。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:20
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_3ec95011:

    # "Class is still quite far off, but I agreed to run with Emi in the mornings."
    "離上課還有好一段時間，但我答應了笑美要跟她一起晨跑。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:22
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_594405c7:

    # "Really, I'm not that interested in running as a hobby, or even as a possible life-lengthening exercise."
    "說真的，我對跑步沒什麼興趣，更沒想過要把它當成延長壽命的工具。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:24
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_fe6629f4:

    # "However, I feel obligated to follow through on my promise to Emi yesterday, which is why I find myself throwing on some running shorts and a light tee-shirt."
    "然而，我覺得有責任履行昨天對笑美的承諾，所以我還是換上了運動短褲和輕便的T恤。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:29
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_483cec6e:

    # "The cool morning air caresses my face as the morning sunshine causes the dew on the grass to sparkle, nearly blinding me at first."
    "清晨涼爽的空氣輕撫我的臉龐，晨光讓草地上的露珠閃閃發光，一開始幾乎讓我睜不開眼。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:31
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_5e2ba028:

    # "As I make my way down to the track, an ugly thought strikes me."
    "就當我朝操場走去時，一個念頭讓我感到了些許的不安。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:33
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_3f7a60d1:

    # "What if this is some sort of joke that Emi's playing on me?"
    "如果這只是笑美在跟我開的某種玩笑呢？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:35
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_ab3db926:

    # "Would that surprise me, really?"
    "說真的，我會感到驚訝嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:37
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_fcdab8a7:

    # "Hell, I'd probably do it to the new guy, too."
    "哼，換作是我，大概也會這樣欺負新來的傢伙吧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:39
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_6204dbfa:

    # "At the very least, I'm sure Emi and Rin made a bet on whether or not I'd actually show up."
    "至少我敢肯定，笑美和琳一定打賭了我到底會不會出現。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:44
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_4320967d:

    # "I feel a sense of trepidation as the track comes into view."
    "當操場映入眼簾時，我感到一陣緊張。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:51
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_d198e095:

    # emi "You're late!"
    emi "你遲到了吶！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:53
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_c07d115e:

    # "It would seem that Emi is already there. What a relief."
    "結果笑美已經到了啊，這倒讓人鬆了口氣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:55
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_37d890cc:

    # hi "Not according to my watch. We both are early, in fact."
    hi "我的手錶顯示不是這樣。事實上，我們兩個都早到了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:60
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_5555e842:

    # emi "Damn. You've got me there."
    emi "切，被你發現了啊。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:62
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_c5397b9a:

    # "Emi is sitting on the bleachers, decked out in her running gear, waiting somewhat patiently for me."
    "笑美坐在看台的長椅上，穿著一身跑步裝備，似乎是在耐心地等著我。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:64
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_4dd68929:

    # hi "I'm glad you're actually here. I was afraid that this was a joke or something."
    hi "看到妳來了我就安心了。我還怕這是某種惡作劇呢。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:69
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_d2f11d33:

    # emi "Nah, I'd never make someone get up early for nothing."
    emi "怎麼會吶，我是不會無緣無故叫人早起的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:74
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_ff9109d9:

    # emi "Plus, Rin owes me 500 yen now. She didn't think you'd actually show up."
    emi "而且，琳現在欠我五百圓了。她不覺得你真的會來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:76
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_a7317081:

    # "I knew it!"
    "我就知道！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:78
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_e6b902c2:

    # "Nice to know Emi was on my side, at least."
    "不過至少笑美還是站在我這邊的，這點挺讓人高興的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:83
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_b6578c6f:

    # "Emi hops off of the bleachers and begins stretching out."
    "笑美從長椅上跳下來，開始伸展身體。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:90
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_de173781:

    # "She's remarkably lithe, almost like a dancer."
    "她非常靈活，就如同一個舞蹈家一樣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:92
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_421da9c2:

    # "I set out to stretch as well, but then realize that I don't exactly remember how to stretch properly."
    "我也準備開始伸展，但接著才發現我不太記得該怎麼正確暖身了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:94
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_90e64c2b:

    # "It's been ages since I stretched for anything, if you don't count my one stint at running last week."
    "如果不算上週那次跑步，我已經很久沒有為了任何事做伸展運動了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:96
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_d14c1cbe:

    # "And even then, I don't think I actually stretched beforehand."
    "而且就算那次，我也不覺得自己有真的在事前伸展。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:98
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_a2d7351a:

    # "The specter of my long hospital stay rises up again."
    "長期住院的陰影再次浮現。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:100
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_42ee91e3:

    # "I can't say I was all that active before the hospital stay, though, so maybe I'm just being morose."
    "不過，住院前我也沒多活躍就是了，所以或許我只是在自怨自艾。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:105
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_678645dd:

    # "Emi giggles as she watches me stretch out."
    "笑美看著我伸展，咯咯地笑了起來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:110
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_287edf84:

    # emi "No no no Hisao, you've got to hold it for longer than that!"
    emi "不對不對，久夫，那動作要撐久一點才行！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:112
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_4c1e8f9b:

    # hi "I'm trying! It kinda hurts a little."
    hi "我在努力啦！有點疼呢……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:117
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_35818951:

    # emi "Ha! That's because you're out of shape. You've got to get some flexibility in you, like this."
    emi "哈！那是因為你太久沒運動了。你要提高一點柔軟度，像這樣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:122
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_9f92aaf8:

    # "To demonstrate, Emi reaches down and puts her head through her legs."
    "為了示範，笑美彎下腰，把頭穿過她的兩腿之間。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:124
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_5a7b7721:

    # "God bless you, Emi."
    "老天保佑，笑美。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:126
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_583b5b8f:

    # hi "I see. Is that the sort of thing I should strive for?"
    hi "我懂了。我要以做到妳的姿勢為目標努力嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:131
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_d45ddbea:

    # emi "Of course! Flexibility is important for any runner. You'll be able to go faster the more you stretch out."
    emi "當然！柔軟度對任何運動都很重要。你伸展得越開，就能跑得越快。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:133
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_ca16796e:

    # "That makes no sense to me, but Emi seems to believe it's true."
    "這對我來說完全不科學，但笑美似乎深信不疑。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:135
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_45fee0f2:

    # "With Emi's help, I manage to stretch myself out properly."
    "在笑美的幫助下，我總算好好地伸展了身體。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:140
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_b4082adc:

    # "I can't help but notice that when she thinks about how to explain things to me, her mouth scrunches up in concentration."
    "我忍不住注意到，當她在思考如何向我解釋時，她的嘴會專注地噘起來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:142
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_acd4cf33:

    # "It's adorable."
    "挺可愛的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:147
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_6ab9a403:

    # emi "Not bad, Hisao. Come on, we'd better start running."
    emi "不錯嘛，久夫。來吧，我們最好開始跑了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:152
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_9242d86a:

    # emi "We'll start off with just a mile, okay?"
    emi "我們先從一英里開始，好嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:157
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_7d892481:

    # emi "That's four laps around the track, got it?"
    emi "也就是繞著操場跑四圈，懂嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:159
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_c49d4f68:

    # hi "That sounds fine to me."
    hi "聽起來沒問題。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:166
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_a3c2cba2:

    # "This shouldn't be too hard, right?"
    "這應該不會太難，對吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:171
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_241fb54b:

    # "A hazy memory of running a mile for gym class surfaces in my mind."
    "我腦中浮現出以前體育課跑一英里的模糊記憶。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:173
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_06beb2d9:

    # "Yeah, it wasn't that bad."
    "嗯，真的沒啥難度。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:184
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_5e41fe27:

    # "Emi sets a pretty good pace, and I fall in behind her."
    "笑美帶頭的配速很好，我跟在她後面。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:194
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_aa29d2ce:

    # emi "Try to keep up, okay Hisao?"
    emi "試著跟上喔，久夫？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:196
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_475aca2e:

    # hi "Roger."
    hi "收到。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:205
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_f6b3ec53:

    # "We round the first curve without incident, though I can already feel my heart rate increasing slightly."
    "我們順利地跑過第一個彎道，不過我已經能感覺到心跳稍微加快了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:207
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_3b992da6:

    # "By the second curve, I've started to breathe through my mouth."
    "到了第二個彎道，我開始用嘴巴呼吸。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:209
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_74a67ca5:

    # "Emi doesn't even seem to be breaking a sweat."
    "笑美看起來連汗都沒流一滴。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:211
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_b2c0364a:

    # "As if to punctuate her superiority, she turns around and starts running backwards."
    "彷彿為了強調她的優越感，她轉過身來，開始倒著跑。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:218
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_ee563799:

    # emi "Are you doing okay, Hisao?"
    emi "你還好嗎，久夫？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:220
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_8a78c4e7:

    # hi "Never… better."
    hi "再好……不過了……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:225
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_40dc2964:

    # emi "Oh really? Maybe I should speed up then, hmm?"
    emi "哦，真的嗎？那我是不是該加速了啊？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:227
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_23b17eca:

    # hi "Oh… no, …wouldn't want you…"
    hi "哦……不，……不想讓妳……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:229
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_d1f5d9c4:

    # hi "…to… overex…ert yourself."
    hi "……太……勉強……自己。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:231
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_ba143103:

    # "My heavy panting and wheezing makes the statement less convincing than I had hoped. Emi simply smiles and turns around again."
    "我沉重的喘息聲讓這句話聽起來比我預期的更沒說服力。笑美只是笑了笑，又轉了回去。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:236
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_731ab6b5:

    # emi "You're the boss, Hisao. We'll stay at this pace."
    emi "你說了算，久夫。我們就維持這樣的速度吧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:245
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_b1675a0a:

    # "I get the feeling that I'm being mocked."
    "我有種被小看了的感覺……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:247
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_49ed3f0d:

    # "If I weren't in such terrible shape, I'd probably feel offended."
    "要不是我身體狀況這麼差，我大概會覺得被冒犯了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:249
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_fdb200c3:

    # "By the third lap, my breath is coming in ragged gasps."
    "到了第三圈，我的呼吸變得急促而不規則。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:251
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_9c0e15d5:

    # "I'm also awash in my own sweat. Gross."
    "我也全身是汗。真噁心。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:253
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_f25d15c3:

    # "We round the curve to start our fourth lap, and Emi looks back at me with a grin."
    "我們轉過彎道，開始第四圈，笑美回頭對我咧嘴一笑。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:263
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_4269ca92:

    # emi "Here we go!"
    emi "要上囉！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:274
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_f7e7b32a:

    # "She takes off at blinding speed while I stubbornly stick to my slower pace."
    "她以迅雷不及掩耳之勢突然加速，而我則不得已地繼續保持著原先的龜速。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:276
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_7c1ae27f:

    # "By the time I get to the first turn, she's already rounding the second."
    "等我跑到第一個彎道時，她已經在過第二個彎了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:278
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_ed0cee80:

    # "As I struggle across the back stretch, Emi continues running and catches up to me."
    "當我奮力跑過後段直線跑道時，笑美繼續跑著，並追上了我。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:290
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_e1bc1806:

    # emi "Come on, Hisao! You can do it!"
    emi "加油，久夫！你可以的！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:299
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_0c9f33ca:

    # "I'd answer her, but I'm too focused on getting air into my lungs and ignoring the burning in my leg muscles."
    "我很想回答她，但我太專注於吸氣到肺裡，以及忽略腿部肌肉的灼熱感。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:301
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_f064afaf:

    # "Part of me wants to say something like 'Maybe {b}you{/b} can, but I'm about to die here.'"
    "我心裡有一部分想說：「或許{b}妳{/b}可以，但我快死在這裡了。」"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:303
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_a7a08043:

    # "But again, I doubt I can actually form words right now."
    "不過話說回來，我懷疑我現在根本說不出話來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:305
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_dda8a66c:

    # "Emi keeps pace with me as I round the second turn and cross the finish line."
    "在我轉過第二個彎道並衝過終點線時，笑美一直陪在我身邊。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:317
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_2a941404:

    # "Her sprint seems to have gotten her sweating."
    "她的加速衝刺似乎終於讓她流了點汗。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:319
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_e9e42e5c:

    # "It's actually caused her shirt to turn slightly translucent. It seems she wears a black sports bra."
    "汗水甚至讓她的上衣變得有點半透明。看來她穿的是黑色的運動內衣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:321
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_0ad1f566:

    # "I feel a vague stab of guilt for being the sort of guy who stares at a girl's chest, but my legs and chest are burning so badly I can't bring myself to care that much."
    "身為一個會盯著女孩胸部看的傢伙，我感到一絲罪惡感，但我的腿和胸口燒得太難受了，實在沒心力管那麼多了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:326
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_e4230a0e:

    # emi "Not bad for a first effort, Hisao."
    emi "第一次跑這樣算不錯了，久夫。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:330
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_2602d027:

    # hi "Ki— …kind of you… to say… so."
    hi "謝……謝謝妳……這麼……說。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:332
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_2bf2734c:

    # "Emi seems to be, if not out of breath, at least breathing a little more heavily than she was before we started running."
    "笑美就算不到上氣不接下氣，至少呼吸也比我們開跑前沉重了一些。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:334
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_7d0abb7f:

    # "It must have been the sprint that did it."
    "一定是那段衝刺造成的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:339
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_93ff6411:

    # emi "Hey, I've got to get a few sprints in. You should walk around the track to cool down."
    emi "嘿，我還得再多跑幾圈。你應該繞著操場走一走，緩和一下。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:341
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_f7f5c16c:

    # emi "Then we can stretch out, and we'll be all done, okay?"
    emi "然後我們可以做伸展，就大功告成了，好嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:343
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_2fba0c0a:

    # hi "Sounds great."
    hi "聽起來很棒。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:345
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_1e8987af:

    # "My legs are on fire, and my breathing is still heavy, but surprisingly my heart seems to be taking the strain well."
    "我的腿像火在燒，呼吸依然沉重，但出乎意料的是，我的心臟似乎承受得住這份壓力。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:347
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_7c5b4b2c:

    # "Another triumph of medical science, I suppose."
    "我想，這算是醫學的又一次勝利吧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:352
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_c4d7abb1:

    # emi "You should put your hands behind your head. It makes it easier to catch your breath."
    emi "你應該把手放在頭後面。這樣比較容易喘過氣來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:363
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_2b48142f:

    # "Surprisingly, she's right. I begin to stroll around the track, happy to feel my breath coming back to me."
    "她說的是真的呢。我開始緩步走在跑道上，感覺到自己的呼吸頻率在慢慢恢復正常。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:377
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_99c9b315:

    # "There's a blur as Emi sprints by me."
    "當笑美從我身邊跑過時，我只看到了一層殘影。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:379
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_7ab57c57:

    # "Watching her run is absolutely fascinating."
    "看著她跑步真是很奇妙。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:381
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_1ec3e2d4:

    # "It's not just because she's on prosthetics, though that is interesting."
    "這並不只是因為她穿著義肢，儘管那也挺有意思的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:388
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_5cc3f529:

    # "The really interesting thing is the way her face changes."
    "最有意思的地方是在於她面部表情的變化。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:390
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_018b49e7:

    # "I can only catch glimpses of it as she runs by, but her eyes seem to come alive with a sort of fierce joy."
    "雖然我只能勉強在她跑過時瞥見一眼，我看到她的眼睛充滿活力而炯炯有神。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:392
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_29c26b7d:

    # "It's as if there's nothing else in the world but her and the track."
    "就彷彿，整個世界上除了她和跑道之外的一切都不存在一樣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:401
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_7469cb79:

    # "By the time I've gotten to the final stretch, Emi seems to have finished her sprinting."
    "等我快做完一整套伸展運動後，笑美似乎也終於跑完了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:403
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_f3fa0552:

    # "She's breathing heavily now, but she's wearing a satisfied grin on her face. She waves to me cheerily as I near her."
    "她現在也氣喘吁吁的了，但臉上有一副滿足的笑容。看到我朝她走去時，她高興地向我招了招手。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:408
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_7728289a:

    # emi "Feeling better, right?"
    emi "怎樣？感覺好些了吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:410
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_3f3c5d2a:

    # hi "Actually, yeah."
    hi "嗯，真的呢。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:415
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_68cd6140:

    # emi "D'you want to take another lap around with me? I've got to cool down too, you know."
    emi "要不要跟我再走一圈？我也得緩和一下啊。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:417
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_d04a9ce4:

    # "Part of me would rather sit down, and not move, but something tells me that would be a bad idea."
    "我內心某處更寧願坐下動也不動，但有種感覺告訴我那可能不是個好主意。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:419
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_1159e43e:

    # "Besides, if I sit down, there may be no getting back up again."
    "而且如果我坐下了，可能就再也起不來了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:421
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_8bce8989:

    # hi "Sure, why not?"
    hi "好啊，有何不可？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:423
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_b6fb0dea:

    # "Emi's got her hands behind her head now as well, which makes her seem very relaxed."
    "笑美現在也把手放在頭後面，這讓她看起來非常放鬆。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:425
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_2f23bafe:

    # "The positioning of her arms also pulls her shirt upwards ever-so-slightly so that I can see a small strip of her belly."
    "她手臂的姿勢也讓她的上衣微微向上拉起，讓我能看到一小截她的肚子。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:427
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_0c84fbdb:

    # "I do my best to act the gentleman and not look, but the contrast of her skin against her red running shorts is rather arresting."
    "我盡力表現得像個紳士，不去偷看，但她的膚色和紅色運動短褲的對比實在很引人注目。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:432
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_14ee9e36:

    # emi "So how do you feel, Hisao?"
    emi "所以你感覺如何，久夫？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:434
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_88e0c47e:

    # hi "Surprisingly good, actually. I'm sore and tired, but… surprisingly good."
    hi "其實，出乎意料的好。我很痠痛也很累，但……出乎意料的好。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:436
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_7f0eb8a3:

    # "As soon as I say it, I realize that it's true."
    "我一說出口，就意識到這是真的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:438
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_62f7c95d:

    # "Sure, part of me wants to lay down and die, but I feel like I've accomplished something."
    "當然，我有一部分想躺下等死，但我覺得自己完成了一件事。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:440
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_4c7bc358:

    # "It's almost like a glow throughout my body that persists despite the soreness."
    "那幾乎像是一種遍佈全身的光芒，儘管痠痛卻依然存在。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:445
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_a9ffb58f:

    # emi "Yeah, that's the runner's high."
    emi "嗯，那就是跑者的愉悅感。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:447
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_90c06fef:

    # hi "Runner's high?"
    hi "跑者的愉悅感？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:452
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_04c79d5b:

    # emi "Yeah, it has something to do with… adrenaline?"
    emi "對，跟那個……腎上腺素有關？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:454
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_a062f3d0:

    # "Emi thinks for a moment as we walk, trying to remember."
    "我們走著的時候，笑美想了一下，試圖回憶起來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:459
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_df0aad5a:

    # "Then she shrugs and grins at me."
    "然後她聳聳肩，對我咧嘴一笑。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:464
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_3e5f464d:

    # emi "I don't actually remember. It's a good feeling though, isn't it?"
    emi "我其實不記得了。不過那感覺很棒，不是嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:472
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_12c594b2:

    # emi "Better than sex, right?"
    emi "比做愛還爽，對吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:474
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_c449a224:

    # "I open my mouth to respond shortly before processing what she's just said."
    "我張開嘴正要回應，隨即才意識到她剛說了什麼。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:476
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_35c4f685:

    # hi "…"
    hi "……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:478
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_a11d8922:

    # "Emi watches my face for a few moments before bursting into laughter."
    "笑美盯著我的臉看了幾秒，然後爆笑出聲。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:485
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_771ee69f:

    # emi "Sorry, sorry! I couldn't resist! You're just too easy!"
    emi "抱歉抱歉～我忍不住了！你太容易被捉弄了！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:487
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_70c6bd92:

    # hi "Why did I agree to run with you again?"
    hi "我當初到底是為什麼答應跟妳一起跑步的？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:489
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_d0a47d93:

    # "Emi just laughs harder. She takes a hold of my forearm and tilts it, allowing her to get a better view of my watch. Her face changes the moment she sees the time."
    "笑美只是笑得更厲害了。她抓住我的前臂，把它傾斜過來，好讓她能更清楚地看到我的手錶。她一看到時間，臉色就變了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:494
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_367b08ea:

    # emi "Oh no! We'd better get a move on, Hisao!"
    emi "喔不！我們得快點了，久夫！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:499
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_e3e60f60:

    # emi "Class is in an hour, and I need to shower!"
    emi "再一小時就上課了，我還得洗澡！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:501
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_0fbc5506:

    # hi "I should probably do that as well…"
    hi "我也該去……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:506
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_95b3e36d:

    # emi "I need to see the nurse, too… maybe he'll write me a note for being late!"
    emi "我還得去看校醫……或許他會幫我開張遲到證明！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:508
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_a7df11f7:

    # hi "Why do you need to see the nurse?"
    hi "妳為什麼要去看校醫？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:513
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_9fdfbb49:

    # "Emi points to her prosthetics, as if that would explain everything."
    "笑美指了指她的義肢，好像那就能解釋一切。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:518
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_3a925596:

    # emi "It's important to check for irritation."
    emi "檢查有沒有發炎很重要。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:520
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_fca6cde7:

    # emi "You know, from sweat or friction, or anything."
    emi "你知道的，像是流汗或摩擦之類的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:525
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_dcb958de:

    # emi "Normally I only go after practice, but if we're going to be doing these morning runs then I guess I'll see him twice a day."
    emi "我一般都是練習後去的，但如果我們要繼續晨跑，我一天得要去找他檢查兩次。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:527
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_5d4c2b10:

    # "Wait, so Emi has only started doing these runs since I showed up?"
    "等等，所以笑美是從我出現之後才開始晨跑的？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:529
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_324304bb:

    # hi "If it's more convenient for you to run with me at a later time…"
    hi "如果妳晚一點跟我跑比較方便的話……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:534
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_34400a3d:

    # emi "Don't be silly! I've been meaning to start running in the morning for a while now."
    emi "別傻了！我早就想開始晨跑了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:536
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_9df154a5:

    # emi "But if I didn't have a partner to run with, I'd be less likely to keep up a routine."
    emi "但如果沒有夥伴一起跑，我比較不容易堅持成習慣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:541
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_b46ce083:

    # emi "It's always harder to blow off a commitment if you're going to let someone else down, you know?"
    emi "如果會讓別人失望，就比較難放棄承諾，你懂吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:546
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_3569a63b:

    # emi "So you'll be my running partner for the mornings!"
    emi "所以從今天開始你就是我早上的跑步夥伴了！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:551
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_1938da8f:

    # emi "We both need the exercise, so it all works out, don't you think?"
    emi "我們都需要運動，所以這樣正好，你不覺得嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:553
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_67928a08:

    # hi "Yeah, perfect."
    hi "嗯，很完美。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:555
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_aa2f1fb3:

    # "Did it have to be me, though?"
    "不過，非得是我嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:557
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_dd3bcfa0:

    # "Well, I guess I can't complain too much. Emi's pretty fun to hang out with."
    "嗯，我想我也不能抱怨太多。跟笑美在一起還滿有趣的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:559
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_03d5148a:

    # "And she's right. I do need the exercise. Doctor's orders, even."
    "而且她說得對。我確實需要運動。甚至是醫生的囑咐。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:564
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_4447b2a0:

    # "Emi waves a quick goodbye to me."
    "笑美迅速地向我揮手道別。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:566
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_abf27027:

    # emi "Right, I'm off! Come have lunch with us, okay?"
    emi "好了，我走囉！來跟我們一起吃午餐，好嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:568
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_81d99227:

    # hi "What?"
    hi "什麼？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:573
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_e8a4d80f:

    # emi "Lunch! You know, the meal? In the middle of the day? Come have it with us!"
    emi "午餐啊！你知道的，中餐？在一天中間吃的？來跟我們一起吃！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:575
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_804bb8e8:

    # hi "Where?"
    hi "在哪裡？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:580
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_d58d26b2:

    # emi "The rooftop. Rin likes it up there."
    emi "屋頂。琳喜歡那裡。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:582
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_af4d2208:

    # hi "When?"
    hi "什麼時候？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:587
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_086b7aa2:

    # emi "Lunchtime, when else? That was a silly question."
    emi "午餐時間啊，不然呢？這問題真傻。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:589
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_c10acad7:

    # hi "Yeah, but I sort of felt the need to ask all three for completeness' sake."
    hi "啊，我知道，但我覺得問得完整一點比較好！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:594
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_93c4979f:

    # "Emi laughs and grins. I don't think I've ever seen a girl smile so much before."
    "笑美開心地咧嘴一笑。我從沒見過一個女孩笑得這麼多。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:599
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_9051983b:

    # emi "Not bad, Hisao. See ya!"
    emi "不錯嘛，久夫。掰囉！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:611
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_308be61b:

    # "With that, she takes off like a shot for the school building."
    "說完，她像箭一樣朝校舍衝去。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:613
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_7a74aa51:

    # "I guess she's going to see the nurse first."
    "我想她應該是先去看校醫了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:618
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_2bed7b1d:

    # "I hurry back to my room and hop in the shower, only to find that the water takes a while to heat up."
    "我趕回房間跳進淋浴間，才發現熱水要等一會兒才來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:623
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_342c12bc:

    # "The shock of the cold water nearly kills me."
    "冷水的刺激差點要了我的命。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:628
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_34a08a21:

    # "I manage to warm the water a bit and spend some quality time feeling my muscles loosen."
    "水總算熱了起來，我花了一些時間好好感受肌肉放鬆的感覺。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:630
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_9c771fb5:

    # "My heart, surprisingly, feels the least bothered by the run."
    "出乎意料的是，我的心臟似乎不怎麼受這次跑步的影響。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:632
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_bc17ae0c:

    # "I suppose that's a good thing, even if it does make me feel like a bit of a wuss."
    "我想這是件好事，即使這讓我感覺自己有點像個窩囊廢。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:634
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_c2ae5904:

    # "I mean at least I'd have an excuse beyond 'I am out of shape' if my heart were bothering me."
    "我的意思是，如果我的心臟不舒服，至少我還有個「我體力不好」以外的藉口。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:636
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_946cdfd3:

    # "Guess I'll have to keep this running thing up, otherwise I'm sure Emi won't let me hear the end of it."
    "看來我得繼續跑步這件事了，不然我敢肯定笑美會念個沒完。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:638
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_68fadd13:

    # "It's only after I get out and dry myself off that I realize that I've only ten minutes left to put my clothes on and get to class."
    "直到我洗完澡、擦乾身體後，我才意識到只剩下十分鐘可以穿衣服和趕到教室。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:640
translate zh_hant a2_emi_morning_run_61fae46f:

    # "Crap."
    "可惡。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:656
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_5c4883df:

    # "The hands on the clock finally set me free from the tedium of yet another fun-filled class."
    "時鐘上的指針終於將我從又一堂乏味的課堂中解放出來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:658
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_08a359a8:

    # "Getting up from my seat proves to be more of a problem than I anticipated."
    "從座位上站起來，比我預期的還要困難。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:660
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_396a8c92:

    # "My legs are killing me from the morning's run."
    "早上跑步讓我的腿痛得要命。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:662
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_a7d006f9:

    # "Maybe doing these with Emi isn't such a hot idea after all."
    "或許跟笑美一起做這些，終究不是個好主意。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:664
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_4bcb1d82:

    # "Still, the run's given me a hell of an appetite."
    "不過，跑步倒是明顯讓我有飢餓感。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:672
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_75e4d9e1:

    # "I'm halfway down the hallway to the cafeteria when I remember that I've got my lunch with me."
    "我向著餐廳走去，到半路上才想起我有帶午餐。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:674
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_c03d6341:

    # "My parents saw fit to provide me with some prepackaged stuff when I moved in, and a good thing too."
    "我搬進來時，爸媽知道我的個性，幫我準備了一些即食食品。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:676
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_21262c67:

    # "The hallway is packed with students headed for the cafeteria."
    "走廊上擠滿了前往餐廳的學生。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:678
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_dcaec1c2:

    # "Going back is like swimming upstream - but I've got an appointment to keep on the rooftop."
    "往回走就像逆流而上——但我在屋頂上有個約會。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:685
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_892e4ffc:

    # "It takes me a moment to find the staircase leading up to the rooftop, but I'm willing to bet that Emi and Rin aren't up there by now anyway."
    "我花了一點時間才找到通往屋頂的樓梯，但我敢打賭笑美和琳肯定還沒到。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:687
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_ad164af0:

    # "In fact, I think I saw Emi among the bodies in the hallway headed for the cafeteria."
    "事實上，我好像在前往餐廳的走廊人群中看到了笑美。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:696
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_0e22f9a4:

    # "I step out of the door to the roof and take a deep breath."
    "我走出通往屋頂的門，深吸了一口氣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:698
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_d6366ef2:

    # "The fresh air blowing against my face and body almost makes my legs hurt less."
    "新鮮的空氣吹拂著我的臉和身體，讓我的腿不那麼痛了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:703
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_f35d1b51:

    # rin "Maybe if I'm upside down…"
    rin "如果我倒立的話……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:708
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_c6c0a8ae:

    # "Part of me wants to be surprised that Rin's already up here."
    "琳已經在這裡了，我心裡有一部分想感到驚訝。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:710
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_c7ccc17e:

    # hi "What's that going to accomplish?"
    hi "那有有什麼用？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:715
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_c67019a2:

    # rin "Things in the clouds."
    rin "雲裡的東西。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:717
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_85907979:

    # hi "Couldn't you just… look at them right-side up?"
    hi "妳就不能……正面朝上地看嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:722
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_5a5fda0c:

    # "Rin rolls her eyes in something approaching exasperation."
    "琳惱怒的對我翻了翻白眼。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:724
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_95139877:

    # rin "Then I wouldn't get a new perspective."
    rin "那我就不能有新的視角。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:726
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_a776cc82:

    # hi "Is upside down really a new perspective?"
    hi "倒立真的算是新視角？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:731
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_53969c63:

    # "Ah ha! That caught her off guard. Rin looks pensive."
    "啊哈！她措手不及陷入了沉思。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:733
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_08096063:

    # rin "You may have a point. Maybe sideways."
    rin "你可能說得有道理。或許側躺。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:738
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_a869e95e:

    # "As Rin lays down on the bench to look at the sky, I give up."
    "當琳躺在長椅上看天空時，我放棄了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:746
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_567b47cc:

    # "Fortunately Emi chooses that moment to burst through the door carrying two bags."
    "幸好笑美就在那時衝進門，提著兩個袋子。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:748
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_3017a2b9:

    # "She nearly takes the door off the hinges."
    "她幾乎把門都撞下來了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:753
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_a3ba992e:

    # emi "Sorry it took me so long! There were a ton of people in line."
    emi "抱歉我花了這麼久！排隊的人超多的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:762
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_3e4cb8f1:

    # "She drops the first bag in front of Rin and takes a seat on the bench next to her."
    "她把第一個袋子丟在琳面前，然後坐在她旁邊的長椅上。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:764
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_e551a58a:

    # hi "You buy Rin's lunch for her?"
    hi "妳幫琳買午餐？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:769
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_9d9f6eed:

    # emi "Sometimes, yeah. I'd have Rin buy my lunch for me in return, but I'm not sure how she'd carry it."
    emi "有時候會啊。我也想讓琳幫我買午餐當回報，但我不確定她要怎麼拿。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:774
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_aea6058a:

    # rin "Plus I'd never buy her lunch."
    rin "再說了，我永遠也不會給她買午餐。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:776
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_d1bbe7cf:

    # "If Rin's offended by Emi's comment, she doesn't show it. Emi sniffs."
    "如果琳被笑美的話冒犯了，她也沒表現出來。笑美吸了吸鼻子。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:781
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_933f9843:

    # emi "How ungrateful of you."
    emi "妳真是不知感恩。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:783
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_3b0be867:

    # "I'm not sure whether the two are joking with one another or if I'm witnessing the beginnings of a cat fight."
    "我不確定這兩個女孩是在互相開玩笑，還是我正在目睹一場貓鬥的開端。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:789
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_436e9532:

    # "The two girls stare at one another for a few tense moments before breaking into smiles."
    "兩個女孩互瞪了幾秒鐘，氣氛緊張，然後都笑了出來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:794
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_acf1c20e:

    # rin "Hey Emi, do you think being upside down is a new perspective on things?"
    rin "嘿，笑美，妳覺得倒過來看算是觀察事物的新視角嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:796
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_7260bda9:

    # "Didn't I already have this conversation?"
    "我不是才剛聊過這個話題嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:801
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_d81c767d:

    # "Emi looks thoughtful, apparently giving the question some thought."
    "笑美看起來若有所思，顯然在認真思考這個問題。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:803
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_dbb12f5c:

    # "After a deep and profound pause, she speaks."
    "她一動不動的想了很長一段時間之後開口說話。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:808
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_d2e50e91:

    # emi "I have no idea."
    emi "我不知道。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:810
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_28821c89:

    # "Well, at least she's as lost as I am."
    "嗯，至少她跟我一樣迷惘。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:817
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_08aed08e:

    # emi "Hey Hisao, you're coming to the track meet, right?"
    emi "喂，久夫，你會來看比賽吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:819
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_cbd6abf5:

    # "The question comes out of the blue and catches me off guard."
    "這個問題來得太突然，讓我措手不及。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:821
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_44d9c892:

    # hi "Um… I don't know yet?"
    hi "嗯……我還不知道？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:827
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_9e538550:

    # emi "Honestly, Hisao, after I went through all the trouble of letting you run with me in the morning, you won't even show up at my track meet?"
    emi "說真的，久夫，我不嫌麻煩讓你在早上跟我一起跑步，你竟然連我的田徑比賽都不來？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:832
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_2fd656b3:

    # "Wasn't she the one that asked me to run with her?"
    "不是她叫我跟她一起跑的嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:834
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_07dc0a7b:

    # "Actually, she didn't even give me a choice in the matter."
    "事實上，她根本沒給我選擇的餘地。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:836
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_1a5371aa:

    # hi "Wait, no, I didn't say that…"
    hi "等等，不，我不是那個意思……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:844
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_9a9b2425:

    # "She beams at me as if I'd just agreed to give her a million dollars."
    "她對我笑得燦爛，好像我剛同意給她一百萬一樣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:849
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_154a1516:

    # emi "So you will come after all! That's great!"
    emi "你還是決定要來了！太好了！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:851
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_de4bd99c:

    # "I didn't say that either!"
    "我也沒那麼說啊！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:856
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_0f3477f2:

    # rin "I'll be going too, so I'll make sure he comes, Emi."
    rin "我也會去，所以笑美，我會確保他來的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:862
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_4379d478:

    # emi "Good idea, Rin! Maybe we can get some food or something after the meet's over?"
    emi "好主意，琳！或許比賽結束後我們可以去吃點東西什麼的？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:864
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_e6a1235c:

    # "I feel like I've just been conned, but not by these two."
    "我覺得我落入了一個陷阱，但又不是她們的陷阱。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:866
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_b6780cb5:

    # "More like by some outside force, pushing me irrevocably toward my destiny."
    "更像是一個神祕力量造成了，將我無可挽回的推向了我的命運。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:868
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_4bc3ad5e:

    # "…Or maybe I shouldn't read books that feature conspiracy theories so heavily. Otherwise I might wind up sounding like Kenji."
    "……或許我不該讀那些充滿陰謀論的書。否則我可能會變得跟健二一樣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:870
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_2c02e8c2:

    # "Still, I suppose that I've got to show up now."
    "不過，我想我現在非去不可了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:872
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_0295fb78:

    # "I don't think that I could stand against both of them being disappointed."
    "我想我無法承受她們兩個同時失望的場面。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:874
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_1057a31f:

    # "I'd never hear the end of it."
    "我會被念到天荒地老。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:876
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_427cd342:

    # hi "When is it again?"
    hi "再問一次，是什麼時候？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:881
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_813457eb:

    # emi "Next week, silly! I just told you a few days ago."
    emi "下週，你這笨蛋！我前幾天剛剛告訴過你。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:883
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_c396cc9f:

    # hi "No you didn't."
    hi "妳沒說過。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:888
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_95c917ad:

    # emi "I forgot? Well, you won't forget to come though, will you?"
    emi "我沒說嗎？嗯，不過你不會忘記來吧，對吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:890
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_c70556d7:

    # hi "Of course I won't! I'll even make a note on a calendar or something!"
    hi "當然不會！我還會在日曆上做記號的！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:895
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_c6c911d1:

    # "Rin nods sagely."
    "琳一本正經地點了點頭。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:900
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_f74c3152:

    # rin "That's probably a good idea, you know. Unless time changes its course."
    rin "那可能是個好主意。除非時間改變了它的軌道。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:905
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_90bdb41a:

    # emi "It can do that?"
    emi "時間會那樣嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:910
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_4cf85897:

    # "Rin gives a noncommittal shrug."
    "琳不置可否地聳了聳肩。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:915
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_af20b033:

    # rin "It hasn't yet, but you never know…"
    rin "目前還沒有，但誰知道呢……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:920
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_9a0aecd6:

    # "This time it's Emi who gives a shrug."
    "這次換笑美聳肩了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:925
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_3670e31f:

    # emi "I suppose it can't be helped if it happens."
    emi "我想如果真的發生了，也沒辦法。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:930
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_9d32ed2e:

    # rin "Not unless you're a time traveler or something."
    rin "除非妳是時空旅人什麼的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:932
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_4bb553f9:

    # hi "You don't actually think that could happen, do you?"
    hi "妳們不真的認為那可能發生，對吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:937
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_2d6cbe34:

    # emi "I don't think we do… do we?"
    emi "我想我們不這麼認為……吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:942
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_5a0cd67e:

    # "Rin shrugs again. That seems to be her default response to everything."
    "琳又聳了聳肩。那似乎是她對所有事情的預設反應。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:947
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_5688ceba:

    # rin "I suppose not. But I reserve the right to change my opinion at a moment's notice."
    rin "我想不會。但我保留隨時改變意見的權利。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:949
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_35512302:

    # "For Rin, this statement makes a disturbing amount of sense."
    "對琳來說，這句話有著令人不安的合理性。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:951
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_a6da687c:

    # "The fact that I realize this now frightens me a bit."
    "我現在意識到這點，讓我有點害怕。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:953
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_3565aea4:

    # "I wonder if Emi gets this feeling all the time."
    "不知道笑美是不是一直都有這種感覺。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:958
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_cc5152be:

    # "If she does she's not showing it, though. Emi merely nods."
    "如果她有，她也沒表現出來。笑美只是點了點頭。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:963
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_dba1b764:

    # emi "As expected."
    emi "果然。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:968
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_30b4b4ee:

    # rin "What's that supposed to mean?"
    rin "那是什麼意思？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:973
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_8b2cd247:

    # "This time, it's Emi who shrugs."
    "這次，換笑美聳肩了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:975
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_1eea7705:

    # "It's like she's using Rin's own weapons against her."
    "她就像在用琳自己的武器對付她。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:980
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_c2776c46:

    # emi "Your response is the sort of thing I'd expect from you, that's all."
    emi "沒什麼，只是你的答案和我預料的一樣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:985
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_15e372ef:

    # rin "Am I really that predictable?"
    rin "我真的那麼好預測嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:990
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_8272b43d:

    # "Emi's smile seems to border on gloating."
    "笑美的微笑似乎帶點幸災樂禍。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:992
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_44c5b1ac:

    # emi "Nah, it's just that your unpredictability is pretty predictable."
    emi "不是啦，只是妳的難以預測還滿好預測的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:997
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_558df1bc:

    # rin "Well that's all right then."
    rin "那樣就沒問題了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1001
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_e050635d:

    # "I don't get the chance to see whether Rin's being serious or not, as the bell rings."
    "我沒機會看琳是不是認真的，因為鐘聲響了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1003
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_39f8f28a:

    # "I didn't notice the lunch period slipping by at all."
    "我完全沒注意到午餐時間就這樣過去了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1005
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_429a4ecf:

    # "Hanging out with these two was far too interesting."
    "跟這兩個人在一起實在太有趣了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1010
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_cecf6725:

    # "Emi jumps up, a look of panic on her face."
    "笑美跳了起來，臉上帶著驚慌的表情。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1012
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_82f72475:

    # emi "Oh no! I needed to stop by my room to pick up my notebook for the next class!"
    emi "喔不！我得回房間拿下一堂課的筆記本！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1017
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_b37e585e:

    # rin "Don't you wish you had a time machine now?"
    rin "妳現在是不是希望有台時光機？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1019
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_0c166bd8:

    # "Rin seems rather smug as she delivers this line; like she'd just won an argument."
    "琳說這句話時顯得相當得意；好像她剛贏了一場辯論。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1021
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_88db5625:

    # "Emi ignores Rin's comment."
    "笑美沒理會琳的話。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1026
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_bc4a86e9:

    # emi "Sorry Hisao, but could you make sure our garbage gets thrown away?"
    emi "抱歉，久夫，可以麻煩你把我們的垃圾丟掉嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1031
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_ace6a627:

    # emi "I usually clean up myself, but I've got to run!"
    emi "通常是我自己收拾，但是我必須先走了！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1033
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_40be391a:

    # hi "Sure, no problem."
    hi "沒問題。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1040
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_7a5c3d6a:

    # "Emi darts away with an urgency I'm starting to expect from her."
    "笑美匆匆忙忙地跑了，我也開始習慣她的節奏了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1045
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_d25319b3:

    # "I don't bother asking Rin why she couldn't help. She already seems to be preoccupied with something else entirely as she wanders off."
    "我懶得問琳為什麼不能幫忙，她似乎已經完全被別的事情佔據了所有的注意力。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1047
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_4066e38f:

    # "She's probably used to Emi taking care of cleanup, and for some reason I doubt Emi's ever raised the issue with her."
    "她可能已經習慣了讓笑美打掃，不知為什麼，我覺得笑美也不會在意的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1049
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_cf3cd5c2:

    # "Cleaning up from lunch doesn't take long, so I have plenty of time to toss our garbage and get to class."
    "收拾午餐沒花多少時間，所以我有很多時間去丟垃圾然後去上課。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1056
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_8d91fc52:

    # "Misha greets me with a wave and a devious grin as I walk through the door."
    "米莎在我走進教室門的那一刻對我擺了擺手，同時用狡詐的笑容歡迎著我。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1061
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_d436935d:

    # mi "Didn't see you in the cafeteria, Hicchan."
    mi "在餐廳沒看到你耶，小久。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1063
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_a64709d8:

    # hi "Yeah, I decided it was too crowded there."
    hi "是啊，我覺得那裡太擠了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1068
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_bf6f48a6:

    # "Misha's grin gets even wider."
    "米莎微笑的嘴角上揚了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1070
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_876c078a:

    # mi "Oh really? Are you sure you weren't participating in an illicit ren—dez—vous?"
    mi "哦，真的嗎？你確定你不是在參加一場非法的集——會嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1072
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_c9e83981:

    # hi "W… what? What are you talking about?"
    hi "什……什麼？妳在說什麼？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1077
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_b0b0640d:

    # mi "You were on the roof, right? With both Rin and Emi, no less! You Casanova, you!"
    mi "你在屋頂上，對吧？而且還跟琳和笑美在一起！你這個風流的傢伙！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1079
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_878f8a48:

    # hi "We… we just had lunch, that's all!"
    hi "我……我們只是吃午餐，就這樣！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1084
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_37f0ddb1:

    # "Misha bursts into laughter, drawing the attention of several of my classmates."
    "米莎爆笑出聲，引來了幾個同學的注意。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1086
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_29373ff7:

    # mi "Wahahaha! You're so adorable when you blush like that, Hicchan!"
    mi "哇哈哈哈！小久，你那樣臉紅的樣子真可愛！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1091
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_8be903a5:

    # "She gives me a conspiratorial wink."
    "她對我使了個心照不宣的眼色。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1096
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_ae22f87e:

    # mi "Don't worry, your secret's safe with me."
    mi "別擔心，我會保守你的秘密的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1098
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_7b78579c:

    # hi "There's no secret!"
    hi "根本就沒有什麼祕密！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1103
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_cf3afc71:

    # mi "Oh?"
    mi "哦？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1105
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_be5b03a9:

    # "Misha seems disappointed and then brightens up again."
    "米莎似乎有點失望，然後又興奮起來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1110
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_1ece101a:

    # mi "Time will tell~!"
    mi "時間會證明一切的～！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1112
translate zh_hant a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_ff9876aa:

    # "I don't know what the hell she's talking about, but blessedly our teacher comes in, and the class starts."
    "我不知道她到底在說什麼，但幸好老師進來，要開始上課了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1125
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_1cff6406:

    # "Another day of class has finally dragged itself to a close."
    "一天又過去了，最後一節的下課鈴聲宣告了課程的結束。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1127
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_05ca0e89:

    # "Unexpectedly, I managed to stay awake for the whole day."
    "出乎意料的是，我竟然一整天都沒睡著。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1129
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_1d6fd8f8:

    # "I'm pretty sure that counts as a miracle."
    "我很確定這可以算是個奇蹟了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1131
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_416871ed:

    # "My legs seem unwilling to stand up for a moment."
    "我的雙腿似乎一時之間還不願意從座位上站起來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1133
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_5e66b684:

    # "I guess the run took a lot out of me."
    "我想是跑步消耗了我太多體力。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1138
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_74c28be9:

    # "I head down the hallway and make my way to my room."
    "我穿過走廊，朝自己的房間走去。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1143
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_bf52f83b:

    # "I sit down and half-heartedly chip away at my homework for a while, feeling like a vulture picking at a particularly unsavory carcass."
    "我坐下來，有氣無力地寫了一會兒作業，感覺自己像隻禿鷹在啄食一具特別難吃的屍體。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1145
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_4a4598f8:

    # "It knows this is what it eats, but it's not sure that it shouldn't be ordering takeout instead."
    "牠知道這就是牠的食物，但不確定自己是不是該叫外送。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1147
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_232ef107:

    # "I don't think I can take this, but it's important to get my work done."
    "我受不了這種無聊的作業，但我還是必須完成它。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1149
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_0e0c5d25:

    # hi "Now let's see… what was I supposed to be looking over again?"
    hi "那……我現在應該要應付哪一科？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1151
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_64a68944:

    # "I know it's a losing battle, but I fight it anyway."
    "我知道這是一場註定會輸的戰鬥，但我還是得要去打。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1153
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_27ee5ad2:

    # "Halfway through my math homework, I put my pencil down."
    "數學作業寫到一半，我放下了筆。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1155
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_b70242d0:

    # "This isn't working. I need a distraction."
    "我受不了了……得要找點什麼來喘口氣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1157
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_eb28cb4b:

    # "Unfortunately, my options for distractions are rather slim."
    "不幸的是，我能用來轉換心情的選項相當少。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1159
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_6f956c74:

    # "I'm not in the mood to read, right now."
    "我現在也沒心情讀書。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1161
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_4fb48ec5:

    # "Kenji is, unusually, out of his room at the moment."
    "健二今天反常地不在房裡。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1163
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_64fc6c34:

    # "If I go to the student council room, I'll just end up doing work for those two."
    "如果我去學生會辦公室，最後只會幫那兩位當作苦力。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1165
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_06cf80d7:

    # "And heaven only knows where everyone else is, except for…"
    "天曉得其他人都在哪裡，除了……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1167
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_00802bee:

    # "Well, I suppose that's an option."
    "嗯，我想那也算是一個選項。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1169
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_dbb48dbc:

    # "I grab my shoes and head for the track. Emi's probably down there."
    "我穿起鞋子，朝操場走去。笑美大概在那裡。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1176
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_653e55ed:

    # "Track practice is just ending as I arrive at the track."
    "我抵達操場時，田徑練習正好結束。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1178
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_1a4cde7b:

    # "The sun's beginning to dip low in the sky."
    "天空中的太陽已經越來越接近地平線了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1180
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_14cc8889:

    # "Has it really gotten that late already?"
    "已經這麼晚了嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1185
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_42cbb343:

    # emi "What are you doing down here, Hisao?"
    emi "嗯？你在這裡做什麼，久夫？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1190
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_9e7cb374:

    # emi "Come to spy on me, have you?"
    emi "不會是來偷看我的吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1192
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_e69340a9:

    # "I give a shrug. To be honest, I'm not sure why I'm down here."
    "我聳了聳肩。老實說，我也不確定我為什麼會來這裡。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1194
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_c2e01bca:

    # hi "I didn't have anything better to do."
    hi "我沒什麼事好做。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1196
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_9574388a:

    # "I figure that's about right."
    "我想這也差不多是實話。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1198
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_e4a1f2c6:

    # "At the moment, Emi's the only person I can think of who I could visit."
    "此刻，我唯一能想到可以找的人就是笑美了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1203
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_abfddf6c:

    # emi "So I'm your last resort, am I?"
    emi "所以，我成了你最後的選擇了？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1208
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_91b84e7f:

    # emi "Nobody cool around, so I'll just go see Emi, is that what you thought?"
    emi "「附近沒什麼有趣的人，只好去找笑美了」，你是這麼想的嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1210
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_e1766134:

    # "She actually looks angry."
    "她看起來其實有點生氣呢。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1212
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_7b8e920a:

    # "A chance for some teasing of my own presents itself."
    "一個可以捉弄她的機會自己送上門來了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1214
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_0839c18f:

    # hi "Actually, yeah, I guess you are."
    hi "嗯，算是吧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1219
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_c76cf9de:

    # "Emi pouts, widening her eyes to give the maximum amount of puppy-dog resemblance."
    "笑美噘起了嘴，將她的眼睛睜得老大，像是一隻委屈的小狗一樣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1221
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_40493883:

    # hi "Kidding! I was kidding!"
    hi "我、我開玩笑的！開玩笑的啦！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1226
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_e991eace:

    # emi "So you are down here to stalk me!"
    emi "所以你是來這裡偷偷跟蹤我的！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1228
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_7afba655:

    # "Wait, what?"
    "等等，什麼？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1230
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_b5cd958b:

    # hi "That's not what I meant!"
    hi "我不是那個意思！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1232
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_b81a7ea2:

    # hi "Why would I stalk you anyway? It's not like you require stalking."
    hi "話說回來，我幹嘛跟蹤妳？妳又不是那種需要人跟蹤的類型。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1234
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_0faf65ab:

    # hi "If you're not asleep or in class, you're down here, right?"
    hi "如果妳不是在睡覺或上課，就一定會在這裡，對吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1236
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_4c18e95f:

    # "Emi laughs at this comment."
    "笑美聽了這話笑了起來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1241
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_64763d96:

    # emi "Well, you're not all wrong, I suppose - but you forgot about eating. I do that too, you know."
    emi "嗯，我想你說的也不全錯——但你忘了吃飯。我也會吃飯的，你知道吧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1243
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_d3e576aa:

    # "I nod, conceding the point."
    "我點點頭，承認了這一點。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1248
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_043c01a7:

    # emi "Plus I hang out with Rin sometimes too… so really I might take some effort to stalk."
    emi "而且我有時候也會跟琳待在一起……所以要跟蹤我可能還是要花點力氣的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1250
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_9b365151:

    # hi "What do you two do together anyway? You don't seem to have a lot in common."
    hi "話說回來，妳們兩個在一起都做些什麼？妳們看起來沒什麼共通點。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1255
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_a7b66bae:

    # "She puts her hands on her hips and assumes a superior air."
    "她雙手叉腰，擺出一副高人一等的氣勢。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1260
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_52d85d1d:

    # emi "That's what you think. I've got all sorts of hidden hobbies, you know."
    emi "那是你以為。我可是有很多隱藏的興趣喔。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1262
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_210f3a28:

    # hi "Oh really? Like what?"
    hi "哦，真的嗎？像是什麼？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1267
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_6acf9d07:

    # "Emi puts her head to one side, as if she's trying to remember what it is she does in her free time."
    "笑美歪著頭，像是在努力回想自己空閒時都做了些什麼。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1272
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_18627e06:

    # emi "Well, Rin and I go out shopping sometimes."
    emi "嗯，我有時候會和琳一起去逛街。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1274
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_99eb9e20:

    # "I guess that makes sense. Emi's a girl, after all. But Rin?"
    "我想這還說得通。笑美畢竟是個女孩子。但琳呢？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1276
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_514d8e11:

    # hi "Rin comes with you?"
    hi "琳也跟妳一起去？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1281
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_a9081798:

    # emi "We usually swing by the art supply store."
    emi "我們通常會順道去美術用品店。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1283
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_67451027:

    # emi "Plus she likes this music store that sells all kinds of weird sounding stuff."
    emi "而且她喜歡一家賣各種奇怪音樂的唱片行。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1288
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_8e065dad:

    # emi "She says it helps focus her."
    emi "她說那能幫助她集中精神。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1290
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_0672fa07:

    # "That makes a little more sense."
    "這樣聽起來就合理多了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1292
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_e9e15980:

    # hi "I see. Any other hidden hobbies?"
    hi "我懂了。還有其他隱藏的興趣嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1297
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_2a93f3e4:

    # "Emi wags a finger at me."
    "笑美對我搖了搖手指。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1299
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_965d1fa2:

    # emi "Now now, why would I go and reveal all my dark secrets to you? We hardly know one another!"
    emi "哎呀呀，我幹嘛要把我所有的黑暗秘密都告訴你？我們彼此還不熟呢！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1301
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_ad6eb239:

    # "Somehow I think that's all that Emi has in the way of hobbies."
    "不知為何，我覺得笑美的興趣大概也就這些了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1303
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_aadae404:

    # "Still, I don't think my question's been answered."
    "不過，我覺得我的問題還沒得到解答。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1305
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_6138c56d:

    # hi "Even if you do have a few hobbies, I still don't see why you hang out with Rin so much."
    hi "就算妳們有一些共同的興趣，我還是不明白妳為什麼那麼常跟琳混在一起。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1307
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_0a4a72ff:

    # hi "I mean, she's kind of weird, isn't she?"
    hi "我的意思是，她有點怪，不是嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1309
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_ad0bbf54:

    # "This comment causes Emi to laugh loudly."
    "這句話讓笑美大笑了起來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1314
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_ef8f38c6:

    # emi "Ha! That's the understatement of the year!"
    emi "哈！這絕對是本年度最含蓄的說法了！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1316
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_4a7bd582:

    # hi "So why? I mean, you're a lot better at conversation and stuff, so I figure you'd hang out with a lot of people, but I think I've only ever seen you with Rin."
    hi "那為什麼？我的意思是，妳比較會聊天什麼的，所以我想妳應該會跟很多人混在一起，但我好像只看過妳跟琳在一起。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1321
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_0d8635e5:

    # "Emi seems unusually defensive."
    "笑美似乎異常地防衛。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1323
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_4d3031d2:

    # emi "Hey, I hang out with plenty of people that aren't Rin! You just don't see me doing it because I'm not in your classes."
    emi "喂，我跟很多不是琳的人也混得很好啊！你只是沒看到而已，因為我跟你不同班。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1325
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_29e25a96:

    # hi "Okay, but that still doesn't explain why you hang out with Rin."
    hi "好吧，但那還是沒解釋妳為什麼會跟琳混在一起。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1327
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_3856b20c:

    # "I'm not even sure why I want to know this."
    "我甚至不確定自己為什麼想知道這個。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1329
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_07a60293:

    # "I guess it is because lunch was so strange."
    "我想大概是因為午餐那時的情景太奇怪了吧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1334
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_bea7a016:

    # "Emi shrugs, looking for a moment very Rin-ish."
    "笑美聳了聳肩，那樣子有那麼一瞬間很像琳。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1338
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_4554cb2e:

    # emi "It's because we have similar outlooks."
    emi "大概是因為我們看事物的角度和觀點很相似吧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1340
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_84486b97:

    # "If you were to ask me the least likely answer to my question, that would be it."
    "如果你要問我最不可能的答案是什麼，那大概就是這個了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1342
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_c1dd2181:

    # hi "What do you mean?"
    hi "什麼意思？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1344
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_00856469:

    # emi "It's like…"
    emi "就像是……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1351
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_7d266f8f:

    # emi "Okay, Rin paints and stuff, right?"
    emi "好，琳會畫畫什麼的，對吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1353
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_8a2b55c1:

    # hi "Yes…"
    hi "嗯……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1355
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_fc449a6f:

    # "I'm not sure where this is going."
    "我不確定她想說什麼。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1360
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_7f1649c5:

    # emi "Well, I run."
    emi "嗯，而我跑步。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1362
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_d920e11b:

    # hi "And?"
    hi "然後呢？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1367
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_69c7a11f:

    # emi "And… that's why we're similar."
    emi "然後……這就是我們相似的地方。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1369
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_35c4f685:

    # hi "…"
    hi "……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1371
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_57c81971:

    # hi "You lost me."
    hi "我聽不懂。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1376
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_49ec4251:

    # "Emi frowns, as if trying to figure out her answer."
    "笑美皺起眉頭，像是在整理自己的答案。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1378
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_fbb8954d:

    # emi "Well, maybe it's that we do things for the same reasons."
    emi "嗯，也許是我們做事情的理由是一樣的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1380
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_0f638bea:

    # hi "Huh?"
    hi "蛤？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1385
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_263acb14:

    # emi "You know, we follow our passions."
    emi "你知道的，我們追隨自己的熱情。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1387
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_467afdba:

    # hi "So you're passionate about running and Rin's passionate about art, is that it?"
    hi "所以妳熱衷於跑步，而琳熱衷於藝術，是這個意思嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1389
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_909055c5:

    # emi "Well, sort of. Let me think…"
    emi "嗯，差不多。讓我想想……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1394
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_39c6c229:

    # emi "Well, Rin explained it to me once, but I don't know how much of it I followed."
    emi "嗯，琳有一次跟我解釋過，但我不知道我聽懂了多少。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1396
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_1843aff7:

    # "Not surprising. I think any explanation from Rin would probably confuse anyone."
    "不意外。我想任何琳的解釋大概都能把人搞糊塗。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1401
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_f2ad4e5f:

    # emi "She says we both chase after an extreme."
    emi "她說我們都在追求著一個極限。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1403
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_3f3aa752:

    # emi "Like, she's always trying to find a new way to show a particular feeling or something."
    emi "像是，她總是在嘗試尋找新的方式來表達某種特定的感覺或什麼的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1408
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_b1c98b50:

    # emi "And I run because of the feeling I get from it."
    emi "而我跑步則是因為那種跑步會帶給我的感覺。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1410
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_04cdf809:

    # emi "And since we don't allow ourselves to be slowed down by anything, we make a connection based on that."
    emi "而且因為我們都不允許自己被任何事情打亂節奏，所以我們之間就有了那樣的連結。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1412
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_881fdebd:

    # hi "What do you mean 'slowed down by anything?'"
    hi "妳說的「不允許被任何事情打亂節奏」是什麼意思？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1417
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_df5bea04:

    # "Emi looks surprised and points to her legs."
    "笑美看起來很驚訝，指了指自己的腿。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1419
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_3e12ee5a:

    # emi "You know, because I'm a runner. And Rin's a painter even without arms."
    emi "你知道的，因為我是個跑者。而琳就算沒有手臂，也是個畫家。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1421
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_6327fc07:

    # emi "So we respect each other's determination."
    emi "所以我們都很尊敬對方的決心。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1426
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_bcd5c013:

    # emi "And that's why we hang out."
    emi "這就是我們常在一起的原因。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1431
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_c2f1fc54:

    # emi "I think."
    emi "我想是吧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1433
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_3a4ba809:

    # "Well, I'm not sure that made any sense to me… but from Emi's sheepish expression, she's not sure about it either."
    "嗯，我不確定我聽懂了沒有……但從笑美靦腆的表情來看，她自己也不是很確定。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1435
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_cf4f24fd:

    # emi "Honestly, it's not something I think about much."
    emi "老實說，這不是我想太多的事情。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1437
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_03603dcc:

    # emi "We just get along - I think that's really all that matters."
    emi "我們就是合得來——我想這才是最重要的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1439
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_9a0bd601:

    # "I suppose she's got a point there."
    "我想她說的也有一點道理。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1441
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_8da12570:

    # "Another question strikes me, and since I've got nothing better to do, I ask it."
    "我又想到一個問題，反正也沒別的事做，就問了出來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1443
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_42844917:

    # hi "So what got you so into running, anyway?"
    hi "所以，妳一開始是怎麼變得這麼熱衷於跑步的？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1448
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_91f35772:

    # emi "Oh, I've been running since I was really little!"
    emi "哦，我從小時候就開始跑步了！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1453
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_594da9b4:

    # emi "My dad was a runner, and so as soon as I could walk, he started teaching me how to run."
    emi "我爸爸是個運動員，所以我一學會走路，他就開始教我怎麼樣跑步。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1458
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_6891bf5a:

    # emi "It was our father/daughter thing, you know?"
    emi "那是我們父女之間的連結，你懂嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1465
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_0433ebbc:

    # emi "Our own mutual hobby."
    emi "我們的共同興趣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1467
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_0255297d:

    # "A shadow crosses her face, and I'm shocked to see her looking… sad."
    "一抹陰影掠過她的臉，我很驚訝，她看起來……很悲傷。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1469
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_4845b643:

    # "Did something happen between them?"
    "他們之間發生了什麼事嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1474
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_da6aaba4:

    # emi "Man, I don't have a lot of time left."
    emi "天啊，我沒剩多少時間了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1479
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_8460b1f8:

    # emi "Sorry, but I've got to get a few more laps in before I go see the nurse!"
    emi "抱歉，我得在去看校醫之前再多跑幾圈！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1490
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_ce07fc80:

    # "She races off around the track, hair streaming in the wind."
    "她沿著操場跑了出去，頭髮在風中飄揚。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1492
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_0fbb07b0:

    # "It seems to me she's going a lot faster than she was this morning."
    "而我覺得她跑得比今天早上快多了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1494
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_b37e621c:

    # "As she rounds the track, I catch a glimpse of her face."
    "當她繞過彎道時，我瞥見了她的臉。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1501
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_90636662:

    # "It's much the same as it was this morning, but her eyes seem to have taken on a harder edge."
    "雖然整個人和今天早上比起來沒有差很多，但她的眼神更加銳利。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1503
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_04f5d596:

    # "I guess she's right."
    "我想她說得對。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1505
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_65203351:

    # "I don't really know much about her."
    "我對她其實了解不多。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1510
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_32d87805:

    # "I watch her run for a little while and then stand up to head back to my room."
    "我看了她跑一會兒，然後站起來準備回宿舍。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1512
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_5c001712:

    # emi "Hey!"
    emi "喂！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1514
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_c46bb449:

    # "She spots me leaving and waves to catch my attention."
    "她發現我準備離開，揮手吸引我的注意。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1516
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_ffcd2dd0:

    # emi "Don't forget! Same time tomorrow morning, got it?"
    emi "別忘了！明天早上同一個時間，知道嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1518
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_641f55dc:

    # hi "Got it."
    hi "知道了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1522
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_c706730e:

    # "I head back to my room."
    "我走回了我的房間。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1524
translate zh_hant a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_a60ae1c4:

    # "Homework beckons."
    "作業在向我招手。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1537
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_76143a19:

    # "I can't sleep."
    "我睡不著。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1539
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_b69598ce:

    # "My body's tired, but my mind is kept awake, staring at the ceiling in the hollow darkness of my room."
    "我的身體很累了，但頭腦卻十分清醒。我無力地朝天花板上虛無的黑暗中望去。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1541
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_2e0c1f1f:

    # "I grasp desperately for a thread of thought, hoping that I can run my brain into the ground."
    "我拼命地想抓住一絲思緒，希望可以把我的大腦累垮。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1543
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_9a376b66:

    # "All I can think of is how I can't think of anything."
    "我唯一能想到的，就是我什麼都想不到。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1545
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_3631b696:

    # "This is not productive at all."
    "這一點用處都沒有。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1547
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_c451782f:

    # "I wonder if this is a side effect of my medication, though it seems odd for it to take so long to show up."
    "我甚至懷疑這是不是藥的副作用。不過，隔這麼久才出現，似乎有點奇怪。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1549
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_08f3e616:

    # "Then again, maybe I'm just not as used to my new surroundings as I'd like to think."
    "話說回來，也許我只是不像自己想的那麼習慣新環境。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1551
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_c46c4013:

    # "I don't know, but for whatever reason, I'm awake and I shouldn't be."
    "我不知道，但不管什麼原因，我在不該醒著的時候卻醒著。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1553
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_7eccd23e:

    # "This is ridiculous."
    "這太讓人惱火了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1560
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_641389ea:

    # "Ignoring my body's stiffness, I get out of bed and look at my clock."
    "我無視身體的僵硬，下了床，看了看我的時鐘。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1562
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_828d67f9:

    # "Four in the morning. Last time I checked it was only one, so maybe I slept a little."
    "凌晨四點。我上次看的時候才一點，所以也許我睡了一會兒。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1564
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_2293b91e:

    # "I don't know."
    "我真的不知道。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1566
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_3e2bf3da:

    # "I throw on some clothes and head out of my room."
    "我披上了衣服，走出房間。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1568
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_76e023e5:

    # "A walk might do me some good."
    "稍微走走可能有點好處吧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1573
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_c74c10cd:

    # "I'm surprised at how chill the air is compared to the relative warmth of the day."
    "我很驚訝，跟白天相對溫暖的氣溫相比，現在空氣是這麼清涼。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1575
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_5b047865:

    # "I can almost see my breath as I wander the campus, waiting for the sun to come up or for me to fall asleep."
    "我幾乎可以看到自己呼出的氣體，在校園裡閒晃，等著太陽升起，或自己睡著。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1577
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_eff6a17b:

    # "At this point, either option works for me."
    "事到如今，哪個選項對我來說都可以。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1582
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_8051d71b:

    # "I find myself at the track - where for the first time, Emi's not out running."
    "我發現自己來到了操場——這是我第一次沒有看到笑美在跑步。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1584
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_6535d7c5:

    # "I suppose that makes sense; it's too early, even for her."
    "但這也是理所當然的。對她來說這也太早了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1586
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_b190f5db:

    # "The bleacher seats are cold, but at this point I welcome the sensation."
    "看台的座位十分冰冷，不過我現在並不討厭這種冰涼的觸感。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1593
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_50ee524f:

    # "The sun is starting to show its face over the horizon, and I know with an awful certainty that I'll get no more sleep tonight."
    "太陽開始從地平線上露臉，我非常確定今晚我不會再睡了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1595
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_5e32942f:

    # "The sun's steadily strengthening rays start to warm me up, and I watch the dew on the ground begin to steam slightly."
    "太陽逐漸增強的光線開始溫暖我的身體，地上的露水似乎開始微微蒸發。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1597
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_34ea4543:

    # "My mind calms down, a little."
    "我的意識也因此放鬆了一點點。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1608
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_6bd09bdf:

    # "Someone's shaking me."
    "有人在搖我。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1610
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_92a1230a:

    # emi "Hey, wake up!"
    emi "喂，快醒醒！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1612
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_b4a2b0ba:

    # hi "Huh? Where? Wha?"
    hi "嗯？哪裡？什、什麼？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1618
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_b087745b:

    # "I guess I fell asleep after all."
    "看來我終究還是睡著了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1623
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_cd1bd74c:

    # emi "What are you doing out here? You're going to catch a cold or something!"
    emi "你在這裡做什麼？你會感冒的啦！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1627
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_14984b38:

    # "I rub my eyes and am confronted by Emi, who bends over me with a worried expression."
    "我揉了揉眼睛，看到笑美彎下腰看著我，臉上帶著擔憂的表情。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1629
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_7cca9672:

    # "I'm still a little groggy, so my response comes out in a mumble."
    "我還有點昏昏沉沉的，所以我的回答含糊不清。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1631
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_19e4566c:

    # hi "Couldn't sleep. Watched the sun come up."
    hi "睡不著。看日出。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1636
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_c2261f8a:

    # emi "Sounds like something Rin would say."
    emi "聽起來像是琳會說的話。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1638
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_69c3aca8:

    # "I shrug, feeling the stiffness that comes with sleeping on a bench for a few hours."
    "我聳了聳肩，隨即感受到了在冷板凳上躺了幾個小時而得來的僵硬。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1640
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_66f23c32:

    # hi "Is it? I wouldn't know."
    hi "是嗎？我不知道。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1645
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_f52a136f:

    # "Emi grins a little at my (somewhat cranky) response."
    "笑美聽到我有點奇怪的回答，露出了笑容。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1650
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_6366a9b3:

    # emi "So, couldn't sleep, eh? Obviously we need to run you harder today!"
    emi "所以，睡不著是吧？看來今天我們得讓你跑得更賣力一點！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1652
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_4e03a9ca:

    # "Even though I've only known her for about a week, this seems a very Emi-ish response to the problem."
    "雖然我認識她才一個星期左右，但這似乎是非常笑美風格的解決問題的方法。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1654
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_8b420f5c:

    # hi "Hey, my body was plenty exhausted after yesterday!"
    hi "喂，我昨天跑完身體已經夠累了！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1656
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_a610478b:

    # hi "My mind was just racing, that's all."
    hi "只是我的腦袋靜不下來，就這樣而已。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1661
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_a5841402:

    # emi "I don't see the difference. If you run hard enough, your brain will get tired too."
    emi "我看不出有什麼不同。如果你跑得夠賣力，你的大腦也會累的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1663
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_3bf389f7:

    # "I'm seriously questioning the wisdom of doing this first thing in the morning."
    "我嚴重懷疑一大早就做這件事是否明智。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1665
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_62949494:

    # "I don't know if my grades will be able to handle me tiring my brain out like that."
    "我不知道那樣消耗腦力，我的學業還撐不撐得住。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1675
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_7837591c:

    # "Emi pulls me up from the bleachers with surprising strength for someone her size."
    "突然間，笑美用她那嬌小體型難以想像的怪力，把我從看台上拉了起來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1677
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_aae8988a:

    # emi "Now come on, Hisao! We've got work to do!"
    emi "好了，快點，久夫！我們有事要做了！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1679
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_ee027b4b:

    # "I don't actually know if I'm up to this today, to be honest."
    "老實說，我真的不知道今天我行不行。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1681
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_50134bea:

    # "I mean I obviously didn't get much sleep… and what sleep I got was on the bleachers!"
    "我的意思是，我顯然沒睡多少……而且我睡的那點覺還是在看台上！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1683
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_88f944e3:

    # hi "I don't know… should I really be running?"
    hi "我不知道……我真的應該跑步嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1688
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_b307e1c2:

    # "Emi glares at me."
    "笑美瞪著我。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1690
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_acddd7a0:

    # "Good heavens."
    "我的天啊。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1695
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_adbd75e7:

    # emi "What are you talking about? Of course you should be running!"
    emi "你在說什麼啊？你當然能跑、也必須要跑！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1697
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_6a432737:

    # emi "How else do you expect to work out the kinks?"
    emi "不然你以為要怎麼把身體的僵硬感給消除掉？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1702
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_8d135e74:

    # emi "You've been sleeping on the bleachers, for heaven's sake!"
    emi "而且看看你……你用來當床的可是冰冷的板凳啊！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1704
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_03d74015:

    # emi "The best way to get that soreness out is to run around a little."
    emi "消除那種痠痛最好的方法就是跑一跑。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1706
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_0cc077f2:

    # emi "Now stop hiding in the bleachers and get down here!"
    emi "現在別躲在看台上了，快下來！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1708
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_4afc55ab:

    # "There's no arguing that. I'm pretty sure she'd kill me if I didn't do as she said."
    "這點沒得商量。我很確定如果我不照她說的做，她會殺了我。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1710
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_dee3663f:

    # "I get to my feet and hop down to the track."
    "我站起來，跳到跑道上。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1715
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_2ce4f5f1:

    # "The sun is warming things up rather nicely, I think."
    "太陽將四周都多少曬暖和了一些。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1717
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_cf00c7cc:

    # "Emi and I begin to stretch out, and I find myself once again hard pressed not to stare."
    "笑美和我開始伸展，我發現自己再次很難不盯著她看。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1719
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_6aa53dd8:

    # "If this is how I have to wake up every day, I might be able to get used to this."
    "如果每天起床有這種福利，那我多半很快就能適應了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1724
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_32b1ca54:

    # emi "You know Hisao, it's not polite to stare."
    emi "久夫，你知道嗎，一直盯著人看很不禮貌喔。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1726
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_015f864f:

    # hi "I wasn't staring! I swear!"
    hi "我沒有盯著看！我發誓！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1728
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_81e5d4be:

    # "Emi raises an eyebrow and considers me for a minute, as if evaluating my response."
    "笑美揚起一道眉毛，打量了我一分鐘，像是在評估我的反應。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1730
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_bef44fa8:

    # "There's a brief moment where I'm afraid for my life."
    "有那麼一瞬間，我為自己的小命感到擔憂。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1735
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_a646895d:

    # "But then she smiles and laughs, shaking her head slowly."
    "但接著她笑了起來，慢慢地搖著頭。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1740
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_7be98044:

    # emi "Honestly, you didn't have to deny it so strenuously."
    emi "老實說，你也不用否認得那麼用力。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1744
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_73c382b1:

    # "In response, I clap my hands together and go for a change of subject."
    "作為回應，我拍了拍手，試圖轉移話題。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1746
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_71c4d746:

    # hi "So! That's enough stretching, right?"
    hi "所以！伸展夠了吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1751
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_726e445d:

    # "Emi gives a casual shrug."
    "笑美隨意地聳了聳肩。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1753
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_384d34e7:

    # emi "Do you feel stretched? That's really how you tell."
    emi "你覺得伸展開了嗎？這才是判斷的標準。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1755
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_d9d66371:

    # "Well, I do feel up to the run, if that's what she means."
    "嗯，如果她的意思是問我是否準備好跑步了，我的確覺得可以了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1757
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_d95b885d:

    # hi "Yeah, I feel ready to go."
    hi "嗯，我準備好了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1762
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_a27e564e:

    # emi "Same as yesterday, okay?"
    emi "跟昨天一樣，好嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1764
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_bc59a534:

    # emi "We'll just run for a mile at a steady pace."
    emi "我們就用穩定的速度跑一英里。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1769
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_0af6fe3a:

    # emi "Don't worry about going really fast, just worry about keeping the pace, got it?"
    emi "別去想跑快，只要跑得穩就行了，懂了嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1771
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_990cb073:

    # hi "You're the boss."
    hi "妳是老大，妳說了算。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1787
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_12693853:

    # "Emi grins again, and we take off around the track."
    "笑美再次咧嘴一笑，我們便沿著操場跑了起來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1792
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1794
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1796
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_f4d423f9:

    # "I think I'm going to die."
    "……我想我要死了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1798
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_bb36f705:

    # "We're not even done with the first lap, and my legs are on fire."
    "連第一圈都還沒跑完，我的腿就已經如同被火燒一樣了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1800
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_a74ff24d:

    # "My breath is coming in ragged gasps."
    "我的呼吸變得急促而不規則。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1802
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_5af15a77:

    # "I can feel sweat pouring down my brow, and we've only just now rounded the second turn."
    "我能感覺到汗水從額頭上流下，而我們才剛繞過第二個彎道。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1812
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_a151a2af:

    # emi "Come on, Hisao! You've got three more laps to go!"
    emi "加油，久夫！你還有三圈要跑！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1821
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_33709709:

    # "I can't do this…"
    "我辦不到……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1823
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_ec88d4cf:

    # "I can't do this."
    "我辦不到。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1825
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_6e7f40bd:

    # "I can't do this!"
    "我辦不到啊！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1827
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_9984c60f:

    # "I think I might hurl."
    "我快要吐了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1829
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_7b4b9cb9:

    # "Somehow we're on the second lap. Emi's not even sweating."
    "不知怎麼的，我們已經在跑第二圈了。笑美甚至連汗都沒流。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1831
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_2aa10bb9:

    # "How can she do this so effortlessly?"
    "她怎麼能這麼輕鬆？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1833
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_91c9d742:

    # "For some reason I'm still moving."
    "而我則不知為何還在繼續前進。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1835
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_6cb1b25d:

    # "She's like a machine."
    "她就像一台機器。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1837
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_903c560a:

    # "Third lap. What happened to the second?"
    "第三圈。第二圈發生了什麼事？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1847
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_a750ddef:

    # emi "Almost there, Hisao!"
    emi "就快到了，久夫！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1856
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_3b6a2f5b:

    # "Liar! We've got another two!"
    "騙人！我們還有兩圈！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1858
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_89842ec6:

    # "Nothing to be done."
    "真的是沒辦法了……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1860
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_b9c02df1:

    # hi "I… ca… can't… do… this."
    hi "我……不……不行……了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1870
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_1c290a50:

    # "Emi whirls around and begins running backwards."
    "笑美轉過身，開始倒著跑。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1872
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_45c4167c:

    # "Her face is a mask of anger that surprises me."
    "她臉上憤怒的表情讓我吃了一驚。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1877
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_295f73eb:

    # emi "Never say that!"
    emi "絕對不准這麼說！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1879
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_6d0b8e21:

    # emi "If you say that, you'll have already lost."
    emi "如果你這麼說，你就已經輸了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1884
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_7babca53:

    # emi "Keep moving! If you're alive, you can keep moving, dammit!"
    emi "繼續跑！只要你還活著，就可以繼續跑，可惡！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1893
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_b24eb03c:

    # "Whoa, language. We're on the fourth lap now."
    "哇，用詞真激烈。我們現在在跑第四圈了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1895
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_9e454ac9:

    # "She really seems to want me to keep going."
    "她似乎真的很希望我繼續跑下去。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1897
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_0dcece9c:

    # "Legs move. Move. Move. They feel so sluggish."
    "腿，動起來。動。動。感覺好沉重。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1899
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_8e9c8fe0:

    # "I'm in mud, or molasses, or tar."
    "我像是在泥濘、糖漿或柏油中前進。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1901
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_b7c8c503:

    # "I can't go on."
    "我跑不動了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1903
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_536b5584:

    # "I'll go on."
    "我要繼續跑。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1913
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_47d50daa:

    # emi "Final stretch, Hisao! Give it all you've got!"
    emi "最後一段了，久夫！使出你所有的力氣！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1922
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_3f50336e:

    # "I pump my legs as fast as they'll go."
    "我盡可能快地擺動雙腿。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1924
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_1a568b36:

    # "They keep refusing to obey my commands."
    "它們一直拒絕服從我的命令。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1926
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_22609351:

    # "Somehow, I keep moving."
    "不知怎麼的，我還在繼續前進。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1928
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_ee25f0ca:

    # "Somehow, I finish."
    "不知怎麼的，我衝過了終點線。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1937
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_bc26d0ff:

    # emi "That's it, Hisao! I knew you had it in you!"
    emi "就是這樣，久夫！我就知道你可以做到的！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1939
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_0f69a088:

    # "The anger Emi showed a lap ago is gone, replaced with pride."
    "笑美一圈前還在生氣，現在已經被驕傲所取代。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1941
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_38e7914a:

    # "She's positively radiant, like she just won the gold medal or something."
    "她整個人容光煥發，就像剛贏得金牌一樣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1947
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_4f2e8e77:

    # "I stagger to a stop and fall to my hands and knees, gasping for air."
    "我踉蹌地停下來，跪倒在地，大口喘氣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1949
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_c833a6bb:

    # "My heart is pounding far harder than it has in a long time."
    "我的心臟很長時間都沒有跳得這麼快了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1960
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_c4d58312:

    # "I don't think it's done this since…"
    "我想自從……之後就沒有這樣過了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1969
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_0b026d98:

    # "Oh God."
    "喔，天啊。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1981
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_3ff0d109:

    # "Please slow down, heart."
    "心臟，拜託你了，跳慢點……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1997
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_9853f1cb:

    # "Just slow down. Stop racing."
    "乖乖聽話、慢點……別加速了……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2013
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_30b4ea74:

    # "I cough, and for some reason, feel a grin crossing my face."
    "我咳嗽了起來，但卻不知怎麼地，臉上露出了一絲微笑。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2029
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_bd088b54:

    # "So this is how I die, huh?"
    "所以這就是我的死法，嗯？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2045
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_08cbb382:

    # "Trying to stay healthy?"
    "為了保持健康而死？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2061
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_982e4257:

    # "How ironic."
    "多麼諷刺啊。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2084
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_b29d99bc:

    # "I'm all ready to give up right there."
    "我已經準備好就此放棄了……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2107
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_270581ee:

    # "But then, I feel my heart slow down."
    "但就在那時，我感覺到我的心跳慢了下來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2109
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_348769ca:

    # "Two hands grab under my arms and tug upwards."
    "兩隻手從我的腋下抓住我，向上拉。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2115
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_4a7fb1d0:

    # "I look up and see Emi standing over me, with a mixture of delight and worry."
    "我抬頭看到笑美站在我面前，臉上交織著喜悅和擔憂。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2117
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_7f24370d:

    # emi "On your feet!"
    emi "站起來！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2122
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_5dc4725e:

    # emi "Come on, you'll never catch your breath that way."
    emi "快點，那樣你永遠都喘不過氣來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2124
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_dc37cc9d:

    # "Somehow, I manage to stand. I try to raise my arms above my head, but they feel like lead."
    "不知怎麼的，我設法站了起來。我試著把手臂舉過頭頂，但它們感覺像鉛一樣重。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2126
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_a43200c1:

    # "I start to walk around the track while Emi keeps close to me, like she's afraid I'll fall over or something."
    "我開始繞著操場走路，笑美則緊跟在我身邊，好像怕我會摔倒什麼的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2128
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_95a5ecb8:

    # "She may not be far off."
    "但她也不是在白操心。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2130
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_b909c41e:

    # "I feel terrible, and say so."
    "實話說，我感覺真的很糟糕。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2135
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_597d2011:

    # "Emi laughs."
    "笑美大聲地笑了出來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2140
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_b894e5e5:

    # emi "But you finished, didn't you?"
    emi "但你跑完了，不是嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2145
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_481a9581:

    # emi "You said you couldn't, but you did."
    emi "你說你辦不到，但你做到了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2147
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_d5aeb26b:

    # emi "Isn't that worth it?"
    emi "這樣不是很值得嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2149
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_06322bd1:

    # "I'm not sure, and I don't really have the breath to say so."
    "我真不確定，而且我的氣也還沒喘過來，什麼話都說不了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2151
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_465de0c3:

    # "But that small grin I felt on my face earlier hasn't left."
    "但我臉上的那一絲微笑還停留在那裡。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2153
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_6ecd178b:

    # "So what if my heart's weak?"
    "就算我的心臟很弱又怎樣？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2155
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_d84532bf:

    # "I still survived this morning."
    "今天早上我還是活下來了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2157
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_c73e7102:

    # "Maybe I'll survive tomorrow, too."
    "也許明天我也能活下來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2166
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_a3fe2825:

    # "As soon as it becomes apparent that I'm not going to suddenly keel over, Emi takes off on her sprints."
    "一旦確定我不會突然倒下，笑美就開始她的衝刺練習。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2168
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_3a8265cf:

    # "I don't know how the hell she can manage to sprint after running a mile, but I guess she's in much better shape than me."
    "我真不知道她跑完一英里後怎麼還能衝刺，但我想她的體能比我好太多了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2170
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_7e4551e2:

    # "Once again, as I walk around the track, I can't help watching Emi sprint."
    "再一次，當我繞著操場走路時，我忍不住看著笑美衝刺。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2177
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_42c24929:

    # "It's weird, but she's like a different person when she's pushing herself."
    "雖然很奇怪，但她在全力以赴時真的像是一個不同的人。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2179
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_74c6bc89:

    # "Last time I noticed her eyes, but this time it's her mouth that catches my attention."
    "上次我注意到的是她的眼睛，這次是她的嘴吸引了我的注意。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2181
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_babecc1d:

    # "She's not wearing her normal grin."
    "她臉上的並不是日常中的那副微笑。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2183
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_95ac2142:

    # "She's still smiling, but there's a tightness to it."
    "她還在笑，但那笑容中有著一絲堅韌。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2185
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_312941aa:

    # "It's almost grim, like she's fighting a losing battle but doesn't care."
    "那種感覺甚至有點黑暗，就像她在打一場註定要輸的戰鬥卻還不在意一樣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2187
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_11fbdd18:

    # "She seems to be running harder, like she did yesterday."
    "她似乎跑得更賣力了，就像昨天一樣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2189
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_e16fc7e9:

    # "Sweat has started to pour down her face, but she keeps going."
    "汗水順著她的臉頰流下，但她仍在繼續前進。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2191
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_410c1567:

    # "Her mouth finally opens as she can no longer get enough air through her nose."
    "當鼻子也已不足以為她提供足夠的空氣時，她也張開了嘴。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2193
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_1f30972a:

    # "As she passes me once more, legs pumping, arms swinging in time, and her lips slightly parted…"
    "當她再次經過我身邊，雙腿擺動，手臂同步揮舞，雙唇微張……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2195
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_30b4666f:

    # "She looks beautiful."
    "她看起來好漂亮。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2205
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_18bd337c:

    # "After we've both taken some laps around the track to cool down, Emi changes back to her usual self."
    "我們都在操場上走了幾圈緩和下來後，笑美又變回了平常的樣子。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2207
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_6da562e1:

    # "The transformation I saw in her is gone."
    "我在她身上看到的轉變消失了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2212
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_64e3563b:

    # emi "Not bad today, Hisao."
    emi "今天不錯喔，久夫。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2214
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_aa97eef5:

    # "There's almost admiration in her voice."
    "她的聲音裡幾乎帶著欽佩。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2216
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_12f01a28:

    # hi "What do you mean? I would have stopped if you hadn't yelled at me."
    hi "妳這是什麼意思？要不是妳對我大吼，我早就停下來了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2221
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_56cf55aa:

    # "Emi colors a little, seemingly embarrassed about her outburst."
    "笑美臉上泛起一絲紅暈，似乎對自己剛才的爆發感到不好意思。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2223
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_ca35667b:

    # emi "Sorry about that, I just… can't stand to see people give up."
    emi "抱歉抱歉，我只是……受不了看到別人放棄。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2225
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_de2b9073:

    # emi "Especially about something like this."
    emi "尤其是在這種事情上。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2230
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_5d81784f:

    # emi "Saying 'I can't go on' is silly when you're obviously going on while you're saying it."
    emi "說「我跑不動了」很傻，因為你在說這句話的時候，明明就還在繼續跑啊。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2232
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_b4ea039e:

    # emi "That's what this is all about."
    emi "這就是為什麼。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2234
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_ba3b6426:

    # hi "What, saying silly things?"
    hi "怎麼，就因為我說了些傻話嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2239
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_ec3f0841:

    # "Emi sticks her tongue out at me."
    "笑美對我吐了吐舌頭。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2241
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_adbf82f2:

    # emi "Idiot. I mean showing that you're alive."
    emi "笨蛋。我的意思是展現你還活著的證明啊。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2243
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_897e0a4c:

    # "Showing I'm alive, huh? I didn't know it had to be so painful."
    "證明我還活著，是嗎？我倒不知道得這麼痛苦。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2245
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_7c1c837b:

    # "But it does feel pretty good, despite that."
    "不過話說回來，感覺確實還不賴。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2250
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_cc842913:

    # emi "Besides, this is one of the hardest days."
    emi "再說，今天是比較難熬的幾天之一。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2252
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_c1dd2181:

    # hi "What do you mean?"
    hi "什麼意思？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2257
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_154c3d7a:

    # emi "Whenever you start a workout, it's difficult the first day, really hard the second day, and then the third day is easier."
    emi "不管你什麼時候開始運動，第一天都很困難，第二天會超級累，然後第三天就會輕鬆一點。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2259
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_53dfac3f:

    # emi "You'll still get days that are really hard, but they'll pop up less and less."
    emi "之後還是會有很累的日子，但會越來越少出現。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2261
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_f0f93232:

    # hi "So this will eventually get really easy, huh?"
    hi "所以這件事到頭來會變得很簡單，是嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2266
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_eff07f8a:

    # emi "Yeah, of course."
    emi "對啊，當然。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2271
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_80d1ae86:

    # emi "But then you have to increase the difficulty, or you'll never get ahead."
    emi "但接著你就得增加難度，不然永遠不會進步。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2273
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_fcf6bfc0:

    # emi "You'll just get complacent, and you'll lose the sense of accomplishment."
    emi "你只會安於現狀，然後就會失去那種成就感。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2275
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_2451ae5c:

    # hi "So I'll have to run more than just four laps, huh?"
    hi "所以我不只要跑四圈，還得跑更多，是嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2280
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_8651c3ce:

    # emi "Yep! But not for a while - you'll have to be careful, you know."
    emi "沒錯！不過暫時還不用——你要小心點，知道嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2282
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_0300e3b8:

    # "A thought strikes Emi, and her face lights up."
    "笑美這時像是突然想到了什麼，她的表情發生了變化。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2287
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_89bfeb68:

    # emi "Got it!"
    emi "有了！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2289
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_d0c47400:

    # hi "Got what?"
    hi "有什麼了？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2294
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_4c017187:

    # emi "You can come with me to see the nurse! That way you won't fall over dead or anything!"
    emi "你可以跟我一起去看校醫！這樣你就不會跑到一半掛掉之類的！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2296
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_9c1ae632:

    # "How charming."
    "真是會說話。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2298
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_8221b7d6:

    # hi "Um… when?"
    hi "呃……什麼時候？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2303
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_8d01a221:

    # emi "Right now, of course! You'll need a shower and everything, right? We don't have much time, then!"
    emi "當然是現在啊！你還要沖澡什麼的，對吧？那我們時間不多了！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2305
translate zh_hant a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_1bc39596:

    # "Grabbing my hand, she's off, pulling me along with her."
    "她抓住我的手，拔腿把我一起拖著走。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2317
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_857bfb7e:

    # nk "My goodness, but you're in a hurry today, aren't you, Emi?"
    nk "笑美，妳今天很著急啊。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2321
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_5ae9c801:

    # "I have no idea how we got to the nurse's office so fast, but here we are."
    "我完全不知道我們是怎麼這麼快就到保健室的，但我們就是到了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2330
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_d5754401:

    # "The nurse grins at Emi and seems to completely ignore me."
    "校醫對著笑美咧嘴一笑，完全無視我的存在。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2335
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_98529ab6:

    # nk "You've got plenty of time to take a shower and get to class, you know."
    nk "妳知道妳有足夠的時間去沖個澡再去上課。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2340
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_b3ad1b79:

    # nk "There's no need to run through the hallways like that. I could hear you coming a mile away!"
    nk "沒必要那樣在走廊上狂奔。我在一公里外就聽到妳跑過來的聲音了！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2342
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_0b539636:

    # "Somehow, it doesn't seem like he's actually scolding Emi at all."
    "不知為何，他看起來一點也不像在責備笑美。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2344
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_8625f4b9:

    # "It's like this is a sort of routine between the two of them."
    "這彷彿是他們兩人之間的例行對話。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2346
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_74b85397:

    # "Emi does a passable imitation of remorse."
    "笑美故意裝出了一副悔恨的樣子。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2351
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_9ee81738:

    # emi "I'm sorry! I won't ever do it again!"
    emi "非常抱歉！下次再也不會了！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2357
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_4e03ecd8:

    # "The nurse and Emi both laugh at some private joke."
    "校醫和笑美對著這個只有他們兩個人才明白的笑話笑了起來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2363
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_b5ad5e35:

    # "Suddenly, it seems that he notices me."
    "突然間，他似乎注意到我了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2368
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_d32718b2:

    # nk "Ah, hello Hisao."
    nk "啊，你好，久夫。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2373
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_63d326fb:

    # nk "What brings you here?"
    nk "是什麼風把你吹來的？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2375
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_0498a2b7:

    # hi "Well, I've been—{w=.3}{nw}"
    hi "嗯，我剛才——{w=.3}{nw}"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2380
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_02b7f261:

    # emi "Hisao's officially joined me on my morning runs."
    emi "久夫正式加入我的晨跑行列了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2382
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_7d47f3a6:

    # "I start to explain, but Emi cuts me off."
    "我正要解釋，但被笑美打斷了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2387
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_e2cc116b:

    # emi "I thought he might need to visit you so that he doesn't die or anything."
    emi "我想他可能需要來看看你，這樣他才不會死掉之類的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2392
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_bc997636:

    # "The nurse raises his eyebrows in mock horror."
    "校醫揚起眉毛，裝出一副驚恐的樣子。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2394
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_5e0c0172:

    # nk "Yes, that would certainly put me out of a job fast, wouldn't it?"
    nk "啊，那樣我肯定很快就失業了，對吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2400
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_766efe82:

    # nk "Well then Hisao, let's have a look at you."
    nk "那麼久夫，讓我來看看你吧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2402
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_45f886f3:

    # nk "Lift up your shirt, would you?"
    nk "把你的上衣掀起來，好嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2404
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_042ba446:

    # "I'm suddenly very conscious of the fact that Emi's in the room with me and blush in spite of myself."
    "我突然意識到笑美和我同在一個房間裡，不由自主地臉紅了起來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2406
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_dc7d82f2:

    # "The nurse seems to sense my discomfort, but it only seems to amuse him."
    "校醫似乎察覺到我的不自在，但這似乎只讓他覺得好笑。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2411
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_aa95d5d6:

    # nk "A bit shy, are we?"
    nk "有點害羞啊？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2413
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_d72d846c:

    # "He makes an apologetic bow to Emi."
    "他向笑美歉意地鞠了個躬。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2415
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_2b288b76:

    # nk "Sorry Emi, I tried to get you a free show, but it doesn't seem to have worked."
    nk "抱歉啦笑美，我本來想給妳一場免費的好戲看，但好像沒成功。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2420
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_0c8e4123:

    # "Emi stiffens slightly and fires a look of annoyance at him."
    "笑美身體微微一僵，朝他投去一個惱怒的眼神。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2422
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_9ce055ab:

    # emi "You're an asshole."
    emi "你這個混蛋。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2427
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_133c748b:

    # "Emi bows to me apologetically."
    "笑美抱歉地向我鞠了一躬。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2429
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_87645ab1:

    # emi "I'll wait outside, okay Hisao?"
    emi "我會在外面等，好嗎，久夫？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2438
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_2e4ba855:

    # "I begin to stammer that it's not really a big deal, she doesn't have to leave, but she's already out the door, and the nurse is laughing as he watches her go."
    "我結結巴巴地想說這其實沒什麼大不了的，她不用離開，但她已經走出門外了，而校醫看著她離去，哈哈大笑。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2443
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_37329bf0:

    # nk "Still got it! Ha!"
    nk "我還寶刀未老嘛！哈！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2445
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_ed15e901:

    # hi "I don't follow."
    hi "我聽不懂。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2450
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_c6339cd4:

    # "He laughs again, like he's in on some joke that's over my head."
    "他又笑了起來，好像他知道某個我無法理解的笑話。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2452
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_cd7da390:

    # nk "I can still get her flustered. It's a competition of sorts we've had going on for a while now."
    nk "我還是能讓她慌了手腳。這是我們之間持續了一陣子的一種比賽。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2454
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_8042e277:

    # "That sounds incredibly sinister to me, and it seems as if the nurse realizes that too."
    "這話聽起來非常邪惡，而且校醫似乎也意識到了這一點。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2459
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_28bff485:

    # nk "Er. That sounded a lot worse than it actually is, come to think of it."
    nk "呃，仔細想想，這話聽起來好像十分糟糕的樣子。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2461
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_91aabb5a:

    # hi "I wasn't going to say anything…"
    hi "我本來沒打算說什麼的……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2463
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_90bb458f:

    # nk "No no, you're right. I should fill you in so that you don't get the wrong idea."
    nk "不不，你說得對。我應該跟你說清楚，免得你誤會。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2468
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_cca4ed39:

    # nk "I'm actually relatively new here, you see. I got hired on the same year Emi started going here."
    nk "你看，我在這裡其實沒有非常久。我是在笑美入學那年被聘用的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2470
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_62428424:

    # nk "Before that, I worked with Emi during her initial rehab following her accident."
    nk "在那之前，我在笑美出事後，曾參與了她最初的治療和復健。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2472
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_cb507ed4:

    # "Hold on, what?"
    "等等，你說什麼？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2477
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_b855e41b:

    # nk "We had to amputate her legs after a really nasty car wreck. It nearly killed her, and succeeded—"
    nk "在那場非常嚴重的車禍後，我們不得不截去她的雙腿。那場車禍差點要了她的命，而且——"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2479
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_23802bdf:

    # "He shuts up abruptly. I blink at receiving this unexpected piece of news."
    "他突然閉上了嘴。聽到這個意料之外的消息，我眨了眨眼。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2481
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_806e0e98:

    # nk "Well, that's not my place to say. Anyway, we've known each other for quite a while."
    nk "嗯，那不是我該說的。總之，我們認識很久了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2483
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_0024805d:

    # nk "So we have a slightly more familiar relationship than is strictly professional."
    nk "所以我們的關係比專業之間的關係要再深一點。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2485
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_ca08d0b1:

    # "He seems embarrassed, like he's done something stupid."
    "他有些不好意思，如同他做了什麼蠢事一般。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2487
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_678baecf:

    # "I guess he's really worried about that. I wave a hand to let him know it's not a big deal."
    "我猜他有些擔心，我擺了擺手讓他不要在意。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2489
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_2f2d6064:

    # hi "Don't worry, sir. I promise I'm going to be discreet."
    hi "別擔心。我保證我會守口如瓶的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2491
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_4a7248eb:

    # "I had been wondering about what caused Emi to lose her legs, and that was one of the scenarios I thought of."
    "我一直在想是什麼原因導致笑美失去雙腿，而這是我設想過的其中一種情況。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2493
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_2469416a:

    # "There were only so many ways that could have happened, but actually hearing about the facts… it's still a little shocking."
    "可能的原因就那麼幾種，但實際聽到……還是有點震驚。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2498
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_b857b057:

    # nk "Well, thanks. You're a good kid, Hisao."
    nk "嗯，謝謝。你是個好孩子，久夫。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2500
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_d3bc83c0:

    # nk "I can see why Emi became friends with you."
    nk "我明白為什麼笑美會和你成為朋友了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2505
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_3869face:

    # nk "She's quite indomitable, you know."
    nk "妳知道嗎，她是個非常堅強的人。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2507
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_c1dd2181:

    # hi "What do you mean?"
    hi "什麼意思？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2509
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_cf62e096:

    # nk "You didn't see her learning to walk. She'd go for so much longer than the others in the hospital. She refused to quit."
    nk "你沒見過她學走路的樣子。她在醫院裡走得比其他人多得多。她拒絕放棄。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2511
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_59000fd5:

    # nk "Normally it takes years to get to a point where you can even think about running again. Emi did it all in about a year."
    nk "通常要花好幾年才能恢復到可以考慮再次跑步的程度。笑美大概只用了一年就做到了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2513
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_4ccea4d5:

    # "He almost seems proud of her, like a father who watches his daughter win a competition or something."
    "他看起來幾乎是在為她感到驕傲，就像一位父親看著女兒贏得比賽之類的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2518
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_d7c93411:

    # nk "Hell, she'd probably have done it faster if not for the fact that we wouldn't let her."
    nk "天啊，要不是我們不讓她那麼做，她可能還會更快。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2520
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_c2a0fa04:

    # hi "Wouldn't let her? Why not?"
    hi "不讓她？為什麼？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2527
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_fde6c471:

    # nk "Because she'd go for so long that her legs would start bleeding where they met her prosthetics."
    nk "因為她會跑到雙腿和義肢接觸的地方開始流血。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2529
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_bd17e116:

    # nk "It's a real concern - it's why she comes by every day after she runs."
    nk "這是個很嚴重的問題——這就是為什麼她每天跑完步都會過來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2531
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_548b4a4b:

    # nk "To say nothing of the risk of infection if her legs get cut up and her prosthetics are dirty."
    nk "更別提如果她的腿被割傷而義肢又髒的話，還有感染的風險。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2536
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_a5e5ee1e:

    # nk "But enough about that."
    nk "不過，這個話題就到此為止吧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2543
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_1d14f7e2:

    # nk "If we don't get you on your way soon, Emi will think we're up to something."
    nk "如果我們不快點讓你走，笑美會以為我們在搞什麼鬼。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2545
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_2c7b1e1d:

    # "As he says this, he gives a wink and begins checking my heartbeat."
    "他說這話的同時，對我眨了眨眼，開始檢查我的心跳。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2547
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_f0057a9c:

    # "The stethoscope is way too cold."
    "聽診器實在太冰了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2549
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_d860dd4a:

    # "He really should have heated it up or something before he used it."
    "他真的應該在使用前先把它弄熱一下之類的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2551
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_a16ae1a0:

    # "After a few moments he leans back, satisfied."
    "片刻之後，他滿意地向後靠去。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2556
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_8eb547e6:

    # nk "Well, you sound pretty good to me, Hisao. You didn't have any chest pains while you were running, did you?"
    nk "嗯，久夫，聽起來你狀況還不錯。你跑步的時候沒有胸痛吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2558
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_a65a2fd0:

    # hi "No, not really. I had some trouble catching my breath, though - and my heart was racing by the end, too."
    hi "沒有，倒也不是。不過我有點喘不過氣——而且跑到最後心跳也很快。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2563
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_ba2b3d3b:

    # "The nurse frowns as I say this, but then shrugs."
    "我說這話時，校醫皺了皺眉，但隨後聳了聳肩。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2568
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_8b617ffc:

    # nk "It's probably just because you're out of shape… but if you don't improve, then you should let me know, okay?"
    nk "大概只是因為你太久沒運動了……但如果情況沒有改善，一定要告訴我，好嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2570
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_ee2a94dd:

    # nk "Don't push yourself too much - and of course if you have any chest pains, come to me immediately, right?"
    nk "別太勉強自己——當然，如果有任何胸痛，要立刻來找我，知道嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2572
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_02e0e06d:

    # "I put my shirt back on, and the nurse leans out of the doorway to call in Emi."
    "我穿好上衣，校醫探出門口把笑美叫了進來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2581
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_007cb285:

    # emi "What took you so long? Now I'm going to be late!"
    emi "你們怎麼這麼久？我現在要遲到了啦！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2588
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_62817229:

    # "The nurse gives me a significant look."
    "校醫意味深長地看了我一眼。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2593
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_d5a90131:

    # nk "I was just seducing Hisao, that's all."
    nk "我剛才只是在誘惑久夫而已啦。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2600
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_1d85b742:

    # emi "What!? Come on, what have I told you about seducing my friends?"
    emi "什麼！？拜託，我跟你說過幾次了，不要勾引我的朋友？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2602
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_bf536748:

    # "I'd expected Emi to be shocked by this, but instead she seems merely annoyed, scolding the nurse as if he were a child stealing cookies."
    "我本以為笑美會對此感到震驚，但她似乎只是覺得煩，像責罵偷餅乾的小孩一樣責備校醫。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2604
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_8404c4ae:

    # "Meanwhile, I try hard not to blush at the nurse's innuendo."
    "與此同時，我努力不因校醫的雙關語而臉紅。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2609
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_179c726d:

    # nk "I'll try not to do it again, though I fear young Hisao may be lost to the female gender forever!"
    nk "我會盡量不再犯，不過我擔心年輕的久夫可能會從此對女性失去興趣了！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2613
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_2410c10b:

    # hi "Not freaking likely."
    hi "絕對不可能。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2623
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_6b91b539:

    # "I didn't mean to say that out loud, but both the nurse and Emi regard me for a moment before bursting into laughter again."
    "我本來沒打算大聲說出來，但校醫和笑美都看了我一會兒，然後又爆笑起來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2628
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_fec5d999:

    # emi "Told you he was funny, didn't I?"
    emi "我說過他很有趣，對吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2630
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_43725057:

    # "Huh. I guess Emi does talk to the nurse about a lot of stuff."
    "哼。我猜笑美確實跟校醫聊很多東西。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2636
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_c3046345:

    # nk "Well Hisao, you should probably get moving. You still need a shower before class starts, don't you?"
    nk "好了，久夫，你差不多該走了。上課前你還得沖個澡，不是嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2638
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_b5173a80:

    # "Crap! He's got a point, and it looks like I've only got a half hour!"
    "糟了！他說得對，而且我好像只剩下半小時了！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2640
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_b91a3027:

    # hi "Thanks for your time. I'll see you later, Emi!"
    hi "謝謝您的時間。笑美，待會見！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2647
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_ef6e7075:

    # "I dash out of the room as the nurse begins to remove Emi's prosthetics."
    "在校醫開始取下笑美的義肢時，我衝出了房間。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2649
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_dade5872:

    # "As I head down the hallway, I can just barely hear his voice drifting after me."
    "當我沿著走廊離開時，我隱約能聽到他的聲音從我身後飄來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2651
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_489805b2:

    # nk "Emi, you've got to be more careful…"
    nk "笑美，妳得更小心一點……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2656
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_9a858a05:

    # "I make it back to my room and shower in record time. It occurs to me that I've already been up for four hours, and class hasn't even started yet."
    "我以破紀錄的時間回到房間沖了個澡。我這才意識到我已經起床四個小時了，而課都還沒開始。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2658
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_f189038c:

    # "This is going to be a really, really long day."
    "今天將會是非常、非常漫長的一天。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2660
translate zh_hant a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_ecd9e0b0:

    # "I hope I don't fall asleep in class."
    "希望我不會在課堂上睡著。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2678
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_0ae872c0:

    # "The morning sunlight streaming through my window wakes me up instead of my alarm, and I realize that it must be Sunday."
    "早晨的陽光從窗戶灑進來，而不是我的鬧鐘把我叫醒。我意識到今天一定是星期天。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2680
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_8531645a:

    # "Emi has kindly deigned to give me weekends off from our morning runs."
    "笑美仁慈地恩准我週末不用晨跑。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2682
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_17743adc:

    # "I don't actually know if I woke up at all yesterday, or if I just slept through the entire day."
    "我其實不知道我昨天到底有沒有醒來，或者我只是睡了整整一天。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2684
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_b3acc230:

    # "My legs groan in protest as I lever myself out of bed."
    "當我費力地從床上爬起來時，我的雙腿發出呻吟以示抗議。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2686
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_0b87aba1:

    # "All this running has really taken it out of me."
    "這麼跑下來真的把我累壞了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2688
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_0f6899b8:

    # "Still, I can't deny that Emi wasn't lying to me."
    "不過，我不能否認笑美沒有騙我。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2690
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_fef2121e:

    # "It has gotten a little easier."
    "確實變得輕鬆了一點。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2692
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_c47a7bdb:

    # "I'd been worried that the runs would start to wear on my nerves, but thus far I haven't minded them that much."
    "我本來擔心跑步會開始讓我神經緊張，但到目前為止我還沒有什麼問題。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2694
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_3da050e9:

    # "Well, it's only been a week."
    "嗯，畢竟才過了一個星期。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2696
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_be08b7e2:

    # "I suppose there's plenty of time for me to start dreading the sound of my alarm in the morning."
    "我想我還有很多時間可以開始害怕早晨的鬧鐘聲。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2698
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_20bea67e:

    # "Not that I could ever skip out now."
    "不過話說回來，我現在也逃不掉了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2700
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_4b3b6031:

    # "As Emi said, it's harder to stop a routine when there's another person."
    "就像笑美說的，當有另一個人在的時候，要停止一個習慣就更難了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2702
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_ae26a29f:

    # "And frankly, I don't think I'm equipped to deal with a disappointed Emi."
    "而且坦白說，我不認為我有能力面對失望的笑美。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2704
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_d2cc60bd:

    # "She'd probably give me those puppy-dog eyes and I'd feel terrible about myself."
    "她大概會用那種無辜小狗的眼神看我，然後我會對自己感到非常糟糕。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2706
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_b240465b:

    # "Which reminds me… wasn't I supposed to be somewhere today?"
    "這倒提醒我了……我今天是不是該去某個地方？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2715
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_2ef6dfe6:

    # emi "Hey, you're coming to my track meet on Sunday, right?"
    emi "嘿，你星期天會來看我的田徑比賽，對吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2720
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_02dc098f:

    # emi "What am I talking about, of course you are."
    emi "我在說什麼啊，你當然會來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2725
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_e3466ecf:

    # emi "Right?"
    emi "對吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2727
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_5dab419c:

    # "Those puppy-dog eyes again."
    "又是那種小狗眼神。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2729
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_2d3068e7:

    # hi "Of course I'm going!"
    hi "我當然會去！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2731
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_93ddc742:

    # hi "I owe you, right?"
    hi "我欠妳的，對吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2736
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_172c8033:

    # emi "Exactly! So don't forget, okay?"
    emi "沒錯！所以別忘了喔，好嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2743
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_042c0a68:

    # "Crap, Emi's track meet!"
    "糟了，笑美的田徑比賽！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2745
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_ea7ea6d1:

    # "I'd better get a move on if I don't want to miss her running, since she's the only reason I'm even considering going."
    "如果我不想錯過她跑步的樣子，我最好快點動身，因為她是我會去看的唯一原因。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2747
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_249ec248:

    # "Otherwise, it would defeat the whole purpose of going."
    "不然就完全沒有意義了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2755
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_2ab2d277:

    # "And so, I soon find myself quite suddenly surrounded by a crowd of people, all turning out to see our track team compete with another school like this one."
    "然後，我很快就發現自己突然被一群人包圍，他們都是來看我們學校的田徑隊和另一所類似的學校比賽的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2760
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2764
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_0fd7c9e8:

    # n "{vspace=30}I'll admit it, it's almost comforting to know we're not the only school like this."
    n "{vspace=30}我得承認，知道我們不是唯一一所這樣的學校，有些讓人感到安慰。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2766
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_6e6ad5e6:

    # n "After you see that there can be {b}two{/b} schools with a bunch of… defective kids, well."
    n "當你看到可以有{b}兩所{/b}學校都有一群……有缺陷的孩子們時，嗯。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2768
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_71e784de:

    # n "…You stop feeling so defective."
    n "……你就不會再覺得自己那麼異常了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2770
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_a4613cce:

    # n "You also stop feeling unique, which in most cases would be a bad thing, but in this case it sure as hell isn't."
    n "你也不再覺得自己獨一無二。這在大多數情況下是件壞事，但在這種情況下它絕對不是。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2772
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_6b20a779:

    # n "That's part of Yamaku's appeal, I guess."
    n "我想，這就是部分山久高校的特色吧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2774
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_b5139394:

    # n "Learn that you're not unique - hell, learn there's a lot of others who would kill to be saddled with your problem instead of whatever they're dealing with."
    n "讓你明白自己並不特別——天啊，讓你明白有很多人寧願背負你的問題，也不願面對他們自己的困境。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2776
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_766cf5bb:

    # n "Some of the kids here aren't here because they're missing a leg or they have a heart condition."
    n "這裡有些孩子並不是因為少了一條腿或有心臟病才來的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2778
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_39f93d3b:

    # n "Some of them might be here because they're as good as dead in two, maybe three years if they're lucky."
    n "他們之中有些人頂多只能再活一、兩年，幸運的話：三年。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2780
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_93679835:

    # n "And that's only if they get the right sort of care."
    n "而且那還是只有在他們能得到適當照護的情況下。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2782
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_b3a290a2:

    # n "It's a bitter sort of comfort to be able to say 'Well, at least I've got a chance of being alive through college,' but there it is."
    n "「嗯，至少我還有機會活到大學畢業」，這是一種苦澀的安慰，但事實就是如此。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2787
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2793
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_1815f73c:

    # "I'm brought out of my rather morbid musings by the appearance of Rin near the entrance to the bleachers."
    "琳出現在看台入口附近，把我從相當病態的沉思中拉了出來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2798
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_8e24cda9:

    # rin "You came."
    rin "你來了啊。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2800
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_128022b9:

    # hi "Of course. I said I would, didn't I?"
    hi "當然。我說過我會來，不是嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2805
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_909aa193:

    # rin "That doesn't necessarily imply that you had to follow through."
    rin "但那並不代表你一定會依言行事。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2810
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_ad62fba4:

    # rin "Lots of people say things and don't mean them."
    rin "很多人都是說一套做一套的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2812
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_fb2dd3f8:

    # hi "Well, I don't."
    hi "嗯，但我不是。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2819
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_6507a2c2:

    # "Rin shrugs. Seemingly bored with our conversation, she turns on her heel and heads back toward the stands."
    "琳聳了聳肩，她看起來無意繼續我們無聊的對話，便轉身朝看台走去。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2821
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_faed3f0b:

    # rin "I owe Emi money now."
    rin "我現在欠笑美錢了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2823
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_e2ba6edd:

    # hi "Why's that?"
    hi "為什麼？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2828
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_196a8af9:

    # rin "I didn't think you'd show up."
    rin "我以為你不會來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2830
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_488e3bc3:

    # rin "Emi did."
    rin "笑美覺得你會。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2835
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_817f336c:

    # rin "So I owe her 500 yen."
    rin "所以我欠她五百圓。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2837
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_57ba34b5:

    # hi "You two bet an awful lot, don't you?"
    hi "妳們兩個很愛打賭，對吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2839
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_9629d0c2:

    # "Another shrug from my armless companion."
    "我這位沒有手臂的同伴又聳了聳肩。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2844
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_9b000ac9:

    # rin "I don't think so."
    rin "我不這麼認為。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2851
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_6f256d6f:

    # "We enter the bleachers, and Rin nods upwards."
    "我們走上看台，琳朝上方點了點頭。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2856
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_7662434f:

    # rin "Up there."
    rin "在那裡。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2861
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_40a2c283:

    # rin "I came out to see if you'd come."
    rin "我出來是為了看看你到底來了沒。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2863
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_18cb290c:

    # "For the bet, I presume."
    "是為了妳的賭局吧，我想。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2865
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_3f0787e5:

    # "Rin leads the way, and soon we've settled down on an almost-empty bench."
    "琳帶路，很快我們就在一張幾乎空無一人的長凳上坐了下來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2881
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_7a6f9b84:

    # "There's an older woman sitting next to Rin - someone's mother, I assume."
    "琳旁邊坐著一位成年女士——我想是某個人的母親。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2883
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_2e0de5c3:

    # "She's got rather long hair done up in a braid. On seeing Rin, she gives her an oddly familiar-seeming grin."
    "她有著一頭編成辮子的長髮。當她看到琳時，她露出了一副像是看到了老熟人的笑容。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2888
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_283b7902:

    # emm_ "Well, this is surprising."
    emm_ "哎呀，這倒挺出人意料的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2893
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_8c864ddc:

    # emm_ "I thought you went to get a snack, not a boy."
    emm_ "我還以為妳是去買點心，誰知道妳卻帶回來一個男孩子呢。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2895
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_0f638bea:

    # hi "Huh?"
    hi "呃？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2900
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_907e156b:

    # rin "A snack?"
    rin "點心？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2905
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_7c36f392:

    # rin "I wondered why I was down there."
    rin "我還在想我為什麼會下去。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2911
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_b914c422:

    # "The woman laughs, again in a way that seems familiar."
    "那位女士笑了起來，笑聲再次讓人覺得熟悉。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2913
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_e46e7cb4:

    # "Where have I seen her before?"
    "我以前在哪裡見過她嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2918
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_61b02c3e:

    # emm_ "Well, I suppose you've always been one to go out for one thing and bring back another."
    emm_ "嗯，我想妳向來都是出去找一樣東西，卻帶回另一樣東西的人。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2920
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_ff7e3f96:

    # emm_ "But I'm being rude! I haven't introduced myself."
    emm_ "但是我太失禮了！我還沒自我介紹呢。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2922
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_745695d4:

    # emm_ "I'm Meiko Ibarazaki, Emi's mother."
    emm_ "我是茨崎芽衣子，笑美的媽媽。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2927
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_d482a825:

    # emm "Pleased to meet you."
    emm "很高興認識你。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2929
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_3806c202:

    # "Well, that explains it."
    "嗯，這就說得通了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2931
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_4ad57b2c:

    # "She's like a taller, older and better endowed Emi."
    "她就像一個更高、更年長、身材更好的笑美。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2933
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_1304efe8:

    # "Apart from her hair being a darker shade than Emi's, there's really no mistaking the resemblance."
    "除了她的髮色比笑美的深一些，那份神似真的錯不了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2939
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_37f76da9:

    # hi "Sorry, I'm Hisao. Hisao Nakai."
    hi "抱歉，我是久夫。中井久夫。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2941
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_430b70b4:

    # hi "And really, you don't have to apologize for not introducing yourself, Mrs. Ibarazaki."
    hi "而且，茨崎女士，您真的不用為沒自我介紹而道歉。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2943
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_1ae3d4e3:

    # hi "That's really Rin's job in this situation, isn't it?"
    hi "在這種情況下，介紹本來就是琳的工作，不是嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2949
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_abe5fff5:

    # "Another laugh from Emi's mother."
    "笑美的媽媽又笑了起來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2951
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_77566830:

    # emm "I take it you've not known Rin for that long, then."
    emm "這麼說來，你認識琳還沒多久吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2956
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_bc4d77bd:

    # emm "It's best not to expect her to remember something like that."
    emm "最好別指望她會記得那種事。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2961
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_59905f29:

    # emm "She's got other things to think about, I assume."
    emm "我想，她有其他事情要思考。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2966
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_42fb76ba:

    # "Rin nods, seeming pleased by this assessment."
    "琳點了點頭，似乎對這個評價感到滿意。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2971
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_7b3561e6:

    # rin "She's right."
    rin "她說得對。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2976
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_226e36e9:

    # rin "I was thinking about sunsets."
    rin "我剛才在想日落的事。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2982
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_fb0bc169:

    # emm "You see? It's really up to us to make introductions and the like."
    emm "你看到了吧？所以介紹之類的事真的得靠我們自己來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2984
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_5f17d9f6:

    # "For lack of any better response, I nod."
    "因為想不出更好的回應，我點了點頭。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2986
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_3579207f:

    # "Mrs. Ibarazaki leans back a little on her seat and raises an eyebrow."
    "茨崎女士在座位上稍微向後靠，揚起了一邊眉毛。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2995
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_3bf3d415:

    # emm "So, how long have you and Rin been dating?"
    emm "所以，你和琳交往多久啦？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2997
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_873079cb:

    # "My response consists of silence as my brain suddenly lurches into gear. But just before I can begin to utter a hastily babbled explanation, Emi's mother bursts into laughter again."
    "因為我的大腦還未能及時開始運作，我的反應滿了半拍。但當我能結結巴巴解釋之前，笑美的媽媽又大聲笑了出來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3005
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_35442e7c:

    # emm "Ha! You're a blusher, aren't you?"
    emm "哈！你很會臉紅嘛，對不對？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3007
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_14a3feb0:

    # "I don't know if there's any way to keep my dignity in this situation, so I settle for a mumbled response."
    "我不知道在這種情況下還有什麼方法可以保住我的尊嚴，所以我只好含糊地回應。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3013
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_da9749d8:

    # hi "Maybe."
    hi "也許吧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3018
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_ca5b56c3:

    # emm "So this must be a new romance then, mustn't it?"
    emm "那這一定是段新戀情了，對不對？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3023
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_e70ce690:

    # hi "Wait, that's not the question that—"
    hi "等等，這不是我們討論的重點——"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3029
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_1ae37bd5:

    # "Another laugh."
    "又是一陣笑聲。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3034
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_4565795e:

    # emm "I know, but it's funny to watch you squirm."
    emm "我知道，但是看你手足無措的樣子很有趣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3039
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_2fbc3b45:

    # emm "I'm sorry. Forgive an old woman her amusements."
    emm "對不起。原諒一個老太婆自娛娛人吧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3041
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_d567d04b:

    # "Old woman?"
    "老太婆？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3043
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_ef81889d:

    # "She sure doesn't look that old to me."
    "她看來一點也不老。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3045
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_cd154af5:

    # "Clearly Emi gets her youthful features from her mother."
    "顯然，笑美年輕的容貌是遺傳自她母親。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3050
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_928dae43:

    # hi "I suppose I can let it go."
    hi "我想我是不會介意的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3056
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_f2fcf1c8:

    # emm "How kind of you."
    emm "你人真好。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3063
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_34cc1882:

    # rin "It's starting."
    rin "要開始了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3072
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_fdd4654b:

    # "I direct my attention to the track, where they're preparing for the first sprint."
    "我將注意力轉向操場，那裡正在準備第一場短跑比賽。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3074
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_214fba4d:

    # "It looks like the 400 meter dash."
    "看起來是四百公尺短跑。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3076
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_ad8eb1ef:

    # "My eyes scan the runners, before finding Emi."
    "我的目光掃過跑者們，最後找到了笑美。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3081
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_33e08575:

    # "She's smiling, with an almost cocky look on her face."
    "她面帶微笑，臉上帶著幾分自負的神情。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3089
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_356375bd:

    # "The starter raises his pistol."
    "裁判舉起了他的手槍。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3101
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_62075404:

    # "Emi explodes off the block, disappearing from the starting line in a blur."
    "笑美從起跑點爆發而出，瞬間從起跑線上消失，化為一道難以捕捉的身影。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3103
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_94fa712c:

    # "It's amazing. Even as the other sprinters converge on the lanes closest to the inside line, Emi surges to the front of the pack."
    "太厲害了。即使有其他選手佔據了內側的跑道，笑美仍然衝到了隊伍的最前面。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3105
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_5386ef75:

    # "By the time she rounds the final turn, some of the other runners have caught up with her."
    "當她繞過最後一個彎道時，有些跑者追了上來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3107
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_7327cf79:

    # "Their efforts come to naught though, since a final burst of speed from Emi leaves them at least a half second behind."
    "但她們的努力也沒能喚來奇蹟，因為笑美最後的衝刺將其他人以至少半秒的差距甩在了後面。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3119
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_9647ba32:

    # "Mrs. Ibarazaki whoops and shouts, applauding wildly, and generally looking like any other parent cheering on their child."
    "茨崎女士歡呼尖叫，瘋狂鼓掌，看起來就像任何其他為自己孩子加油的家長一樣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3121
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_42d67943:

    # "Emi bounds off the track, looking pleased with herself."
    "笑美從跑道上走下，看起來對自己的表現很是滿意。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3130
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_927c7898:

    # "I cheer right along with the rest of them."
    "我和她們一起鼓掌歡呼。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3132
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_f5f2273f:

    # "The announcer (sounding suspiciously like Misha) gleefully gives the results."
    "播報員（聲音聽起來可疑地像米莎）興高采烈地宣布了結果。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3138
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_49aa6f79:

    # emm "I think she's gotten faster since the last time."
    emm "我覺得她比上次更快了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3143
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_7a658918:

    # hi "That was incredible."
    hi "那真是太不可思議了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3149
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_6e0f28f0:

    # "Mrs. Ibarazaki grins proudly."
    "茨崎女士驕傲地笑著。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3151
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_24acd1f9:

    # emm "Emi's a heck of a runner."
    emm "笑美是個了不起的跑者。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3156
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_b6ee50d3:

    # "We fall silent as the next event is being prepared."
    "當下一個項目準備開始時，我們都安靜了下來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3158
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_b628005f:

    # "I'm surprised to see Emi striding out onto the track again."
    "我很驚訝地看到笑美再次大步走上操場。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3163
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_a262c76c:

    # hi "Wait, didn't she just run?"
    hi "等等，她不是剛跑完嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3165
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_e8c4686e:

    # "Emi's mother nods."
    "笑美的媽媽點了點頭。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3170
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_c130b458:

    # emm "Yes, but she runs multiple events for the team. Especially the sprints."
    emm "嗯，但她參加了很多項目，短跑特別多。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3175
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_c19ab472:

    # emm "It's a lot of running, but Emi can handle it."
    emm "要跑很多，但笑美沒問題的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3177
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_6fcd9d17:

    # "From the looks of things, she's right."
    "從現況看來，她說得對。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3179
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_c4a6384b:

    # "Emi doesn't appear to be tired, as if she hadn't run the previous event at all."
    "笑美看起來一點也不累，彷彿她根本沒跑過前一個項目。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3181
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_64ea2cbf:

    # "If not for the sweat visible on her shirt, you'd never know."
    "要不是她上衣上看得見的汗水，你根本不會知道。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3186
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_1bee6ed0:

    # hi "Which event is this?"
    hi "這是什麼比賽？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3192
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_7d1676cf:

    # emm "It's the 200 meter dash."
    emm "是兩百公尺短跑。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3194
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_a9c47c5a:

    # emm "She'll do this one, the 100-meter, and the relay."
    emm "她會跑這個、一百公尺和接力賽。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3199
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_e1f8a5e6:

    # hi "I see."
    hi "我明白了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3207
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_0de8c5d6:

    # "Once again the pistol sounds, and once again Emi flies off the block."
    "信號槍再次響起，笑美也再次如脫弦的弓箭一般飛出。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3209
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_2417e5b8:

    # "A thumping sound draws my attention away from the race."
    "一陣敲擊聲把我的注意力從比賽中拉了回來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3211
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_ebb65b2c:

    # "It's Rin's foot."
    "是琳的腳發出來的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3213
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_801e329d:

    # "She seems completely absorbed in the race."
    "她似乎完全沉浸在比賽中。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3221
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_f49b9658:

    # "Emi's mother cheers again, and I assume that the race is over."
    "笑美的媽媽再次歡呼，我猜比賽結束了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3223
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_941ecf11:

    # "Sprints don't seem to me like they'd take very long to complete."
    "短跑並不是要花很長時間完成的項目。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3225
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_c382c6c8:

    # hi "Your foot."
    hi "妳的腳。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3231
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_e9686c2a:

    # rin "Hmm?"
    rin "嗯？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3233
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_2cb216d6:

    # hi "Your foot was bouncing on the bleachers."
    hi "妳的腳在看台上抖動。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3238
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_8cf3c02d:

    # rin "Oh."
    rin "哦。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3240
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_8e421606:

    # hi "You seem pretty into this stuff. I'm surprised."
    hi "妳似乎對這類東西很投入。我蠻驚訝的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3245
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_d2491b20:

    # "Rin looks at me quizzically."
    "琳不解地看著我。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3247
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_6190fe41:

    # rin "Why wouldn't I be?"
    rin "為什麼我不該投入？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3249
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_dae65d75:

    # hi "No reason, I just thought stuff like sports wouldn't interest you."
    hi "沒什麼特別的原因，我只是覺得像運動這類的東西妳不會感興趣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3254
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_de550c0c:

    # rin "Hmm, I suppose you're right."
    rin "嗯，我想你說得對。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3256
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_056a211c:

    # rin "It's not that interesting."
    rin "那不是很有趣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3261
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_555d1430:

    # rin "But I'm watching Emi, not the sport."
    rin "但我在看的是笑美，不是運動。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3263
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_ed15e901:

    # hi "I don't follow."
    hi "我聽不懂。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3268
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_fe9a74c4:

    # rin "Emi's the most Emi when she runs."
    rin "笑美在跑步的時候，最像笑美。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3270
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_9fcc19fb:

    # rin "You don't get to see Emi at her Emiest very often."
    rin "你平日是看不到她最笑美的那一面的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3275
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_3ae9d7f7:

    # rin "But here, you can. See?"
    rin "但在這裡，你可以。看到了嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3277
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_3fc268c5:

    # "She directs my attention toward the track again, where the 100-meter dash is about to start."
    "她再次將我的注意力引向操場，那裡的一百公尺短跑即將開始。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3285
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_4b886958:

    # "I watch Emi closely."
    "我仔細地看著笑美。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3287
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_befbd79a:

    # "As she gets onto the starter blocks, her whole body seems to relax, but it's a false relaxation."
    "她走上起跑線時，她的身體看上去十分放鬆，但那只是假象。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3289
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_dedaa01b:

    # "I can see that she's actually like a coiled spring."
    "我看得出她其實像一根緊繃的彈簧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3294
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_2ed0b4eb:

    # "As the starter tells everyone to get set, her head snaps up, and her eyes narrow slightly."
    "裁判讓所有人預備時，她猛然抬起了頭，眼睛微微眯起。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3296
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_1ab7f00a:

    # "Her mouth curls upward in what could be a grin and could be a growl."
    "她的嘴角向上彎起，那表情既像貓咪的微笑，也像老虎的低吼。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3306
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_3dbe4dc8:

    # "When the pistol goes off, it's as if she's been unleashed from a cage, like she was always moving at this blinding speed, but we couldn't see it happening until the starter's pistol dispelled the illusion of motionlessness."
    "當槍響時，她彷彿從籠中被釋放出來。似乎她一直都以這種炫目的速度移動，只是我們看不見，直到槍聲驅散了她靜止不動的幻象。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3308
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_d842224f:

    # "It's all over in a few seconds, but in those few seconds I feel like I just witnessed something very personal for Emi."
    "一切在幾秒鐘內就結束了，但在那短短的幾秒鐘裡，我覺得我見證了笑美非常私密的一面。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3313
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_684ddac6:

    # "As soon as she crossed the finish line, the fierce look was replaced by her normal grin."
    "她一越過終點線，那兇猛的神情就被她平常的笑容所取代。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3315
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_e0805e23:

    # "The conquering general returning to his farm."
    "就像得勝的將軍回到他的家鄉。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3317
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_6ca17858:

    # hi "Amazing."
    hi "太厲害了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3319
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_c7970656:

    # hi "She's really amazing. I've never seen anyone move that fast."
    hi "她真的太厲害了。我從沒見過有人能跑得那麼快。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3326
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_e245860a:

    # emm "Well, don't look at me, I'm far too relaxed to run that fast."
    emm "嗯，別看我，我太懶散了，跑不了那麼快。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3332
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_5a6f12a2:

    # emm "No, I think Emi's prowess all came from her father's side."
    emm "若要我說的話，笑美的才華一定是遺傳自她爸爸。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3334
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_3a556b49:

    # "At the mention of Emi's father, Mrs. Ibarazaki looks wistful, almost sad."
    "一提到笑美的父親，茨崎女士的神情變得惆悵，幾乎是悲傷。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3336
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_3c9c175b:

    # emm "He got her into running, you know."
    emm "是她爸爸帶她開始跑步的，你知道嗎。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3341
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_6dc6f21e:

    # hi "Yeah, she told me."
    hi "嗯，她跟我說過。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3343
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_d98d30de:

    # "I'm uncertain as to whether or not it would be rude of me to ask after Emi's father."
    "我不確定問起笑美的父親會不會很失禮。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3345
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_8d484ca9:

    # "But after that look on her face a few days ago, I feel compelled to ask."
    "但看到她幾天前的表情，我有種不得不問的衝動。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3347
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_47fb97a9:

    # hi "Where is her father now, if I might ask?"
    hi "如果我可以問的話，她父親現在在哪裡？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3349
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_85839e43:

    # "Emi's mother hesitates, clearly not willing to answer the question but at the same time not wishing to appear rude."
    "笑美的媽媽猶豫了一下，顯然不願意回答這個問題，但同時又不想顯得失禮。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3355
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_1954442b:

    # emm "He… isn't around any more."
    emm "他……已經不在了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3357
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_d185323f:

    # hi "I'm sorry, I didn't mean to bring up bad memories."
    hi "對不起，我不是故意要勾起您不好的回憶。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3362
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_ff763c3d:

    # hi "Emi just seemed a little sad when she mentioned him earlier."
    hi "只是笑美之前提到他的時候，看起來有點傷心。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3368
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_16e971c2:

    # emm "That's not surprising, considering."
    emm "考慮到情況，那並不奇怪。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3370
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_34d1d59d:

    # hi "Hmm?"
    hi "嗯？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3372
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_6e166686:

    # emm "They were very close."
    emm "他們父女倆非常親近。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3377
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_e1f8a5e6_1:

    # hi "I see."
    hi "我明白了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3381
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_cfc64809:

    # "A beeping noise suddenly emanates from Mrs. Ibarazaki's pocket. Reaching into it, she pulls out a cell phone and looks at it."
    "一陣嗶嗶聲突然從茨崎女士的口袋裡傳出。她伸手進去，拿出一部手機看了看。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3387
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_11150d81:

    # emm "…Honestly, text messages?"
    emm "……說真的，傳簡訊？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3389
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_9884910a:

    # emm "What is he, sixteen?"
    emm "他是十六歲嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3391
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_34d1d59d_1:

    # hi "Hmm?"
    hi "嗯？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3396
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_bdc861ba:

    # emm "Oh, nothing."
    emm "哦，沒什麼。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3401
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_8a9af1ea:

    # emm "I've got to go meet up with a friend of mine."
    emm "我得去跟我一個朋友碰面。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3406
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_1f7c4f4c:

    # emm "Will you tell Emi I'm very proud of her and that I'll call her later tonight?"
    emm "你能告訴笑美我為她感到驕傲，還有我今天晚點會打電話給她嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3411
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_2f6a93ba:

    # hi "Of course."
    hi "當然。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3425
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_622d1442:

    # "I'll admit that I zone out for a while."
    "我承認我有那麼一會兒分心了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3427
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_32fb0deb:

    # "I almost don't notice that the relay's about to begin. But when I look, I can't find Emi."
    "我幾乎沒注意到接力賽就要開始了。但當我抬頭看時，卻找不到笑美。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3429
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_744d1d12:

    # hi "I thought that Emi would be running the relay."
    hi "笑美不是原定要參加接力的嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3434
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_ad0eb544:

    # rin "She runs anchor."
    rin "她跑最後一棒。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3439
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_df65623e:

    # rin "So she won't be running for a while yet."
    rin "所以她還要一會兒才會跑。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3441
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_9a287fc4:

    # hi "Ah."
    hi "啊。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3446
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_4f0bbe13:

    # rin "Did you see it?"
    rin "你看到了嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3448
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_0f638bea_1:

    # hi "Huh?"
    hi "嗯？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3450
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_cd582b13:

    # rin "Emi at her Emiest."
    rin "最像笑美的笑美。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3452
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_da9749d8_1:

    # hi "Maybe."
    hi "也許吧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3457
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_720de3d4:

    # rin "Hmm. Maybe this time."
    rin "嗯。也許這次能看到。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3461
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_f4815bcf:

    # "The race begins, and I cheer Emi's teammates along as they pass the baton."
    "比賽開始了，我大聲為笑美的隊友助威，看著她們交遞接力棒。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3470
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_b4db896e:

    # "Finally, I see Emi sprinting onto the track to take the final handoff."
    "終於，我看到笑美衝上跑道，準備接下最後一棒。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3472
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_8a1384d5:

    # "Once again I'm taken aback by how graceful she looks when she runs."
    "我再次被她跑步時優雅的姿態所震懾。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3474
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_9dc6b057:

    # "It really is beautiful."
    "真的是太美了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3476
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_c5959e99:

    # "The look of determination and fearlessness on her face only adds to the picture."
    "她臉上堅定而無畏的神情更是為這情景畫龍點睛。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3478
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_eba05354:

    # "Emi at her Emiest, I suppose."
    "我想，這就是最笑美的笑美吧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3486
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_9831e727:

    # "But then, as she crosses the finish line, I see her stumble slightly."
    "但就在她衝過終點線時，我看到她稍微踉蹌了一下。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3488
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_68a864f6:

    # "It's only barely, but it's a definite stumble."
    "雖然只是輕微的一下，但那確實是踉蹌。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3496
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_2c15b4e9:

    # "Rin inhales sharply, and actually looks concerned for a second."
    "琳倒抽了一口氣，有那麼一瞬間看起來真的很擔心。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3498
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_e66078ab:

    # rin "Aw, Emi…"
    rin "唉，笑美……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3500
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_38570eb3:

    # hi "Did she hurt herself, do you think?"
    hi "妳覺得她受傷了嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3505
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_bf088471:

    # rin "You noticed it too?"
    rin "你也注意到了？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3510
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_af7ffe6f:

    # rin "It must be bad."
    rin "那一定很嚴重。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3515
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_3032e35c:

    # "She frowns, as if deciding on the next course of action."
    "她皺起眉頭，像是在決定下一步該怎麼做。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3517
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_a3651292:

    # "Eventually that proves to be too tiresome, and she shrugs again."
    "最後，這似乎太麻煩了，於是她又聳了聳肩。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3522
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_0db301bd:

    # rin "Well, let's go down."
    rin "嗯，我們下去吧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3524
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_da48fab6:

    # rin "Gotta crown the victor."
    rin "得要為冠軍加冕啊。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3529
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_8ece8966:

    # rin "See if you can find a laurel branch."
    rin "你去找找看有沒有月桂樹枝。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3531
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_14d0d891:

    # hi "That's not going to be easy."
    hi "這可不是說找到就能找到的……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3536
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_4387f3ee:

    # "Rin shrugs."
    "琳聳了聳肩。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3541
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_75256cce:

    # rin "At least we tried."
    rin "至少我們試過了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3543
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_ff58ccb4:

    # "Well, we didn't really try all that hard."
    "嗯，我們其實也沒那麼努力試就是了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3545
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_853d2b6d:

    # "Or at all. But hey, whatever."
    "或者說根本沒試。不過，嘿，隨便啦。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3556
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_a3fc7fb8:

    # "Emi is surrounded by her teammates, all of them congratulating her on the run."
    "笑美被她的隊友們包圍著，大家都在祝賀她跑得好。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3558
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_b8995621:

    # "Rin seems to be waiting for Emi to notice that she's arrived."
    "琳站在一旁，像是在等笑美來注意到她的存在。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3560
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_c5897460:

    # "Oh yeah, I guess she can't exactly wave Emi over."
    "啊，說起來也是，她也沒辦法向笑美招手致意啊。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3562
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_de08b7fc:

    # "Then again, I'm not sure that Rin would do such a thing even if she had arms."
    "不過話說回來，就算琳有手臂，我也不確定她會不會這麼做。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3564
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_1bea275d:

    # "It doesn't seem her style to draw attention to herself. Or to emote beyond shrugging."
    "引人注目似乎不是她的風格。或者說，除了聳肩之外，她也不太表露情緒。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3566
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_a51f2471:

    # "Either way, I'm not willing to wait, so I wave to Emi, who looks up and grins happily at me - er, us."
    "無論如何，我可不想等，所以我向笑美揮了揮手，她抬起頭，開心地對我——呃，我們——笑了笑。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3578
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_69687d3f:

    # emi "Hey, you showed up!"
    emi "嘿，你來啦！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3583
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_a9e97cf6:

    # emi "Guess Rin owes me money, huh?"
    emi "這麼一來琳就欠我錢了呢，呵呵。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3588
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_962c8615:

    # rin "We would have brought you a crown of laurels, but Hisao didn't find one."
    rin "我們本來想帶個桂冠給妳，但是久夫沒找到。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3593
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_57f0895e:

    # hi "Hey, neither did you."
    hi "喂，妳也沒找到啊。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3598
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_68d3c7a6:

    # rin "It wasn't my job to look."
    rin "找東西什麼的不是我的工作。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3600
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_478e7a49:

    # hi "When did we assign jobs?"
    hi "我們啥時候這麼分工了？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3605
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_51225eda:

    # rin "When I said 'See if you can find a laurel branch.'"
    rin "在我說「你去找找看有沒有月桂樹枝」的時候。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3610
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_f73cd465:

    # rin "Try to keep up."
    rin "用心點啊。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3612
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_86af4c08:

    # "I shrug. Guess Rin's rubbing off on me."
    "我聳了聳肩。看來我被琳影響了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3614
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_202ec59f:

    # hi "Seems it's my fault after all, Emi."
    hi "笑美，看來終究是我的錯。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3620
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_4e83c593:

    # "Emi laughs at Rin and me."
    "笑美看著我和琳笑了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3625
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_2beaa6fc:

    # emi "It's okay, I'm sure you'll make it up to me somehow."
    emi "沒關係，我相信你總會用某種方式補償我的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3630
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_5a036de1:

    # hi "Uh, sure."
    hi "呃，當然。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3636
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_a579d2cf:

    # emi "Good! So, how'd I look?"
    emi "好！所以，我看起來怎麼樣？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3641
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_3ff78a0b:

    # "I stop myself from blurting out 'beautiful' or 'amazing' and settle for the substantially safer 'very impressive.'"
    "我忍住沒脫口說出「太美了」或「太棒了」，而是選擇了安全得多的「非常令人印象深刻」。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3646
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_7699e576:

    # "Emi seems pleased with this assessment."
    "笑美似乎對這個評價很滿意。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3648
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_9472d192:

    # "I don't mention how much more impressive her performance is given her lack of legs. I figure she knows that already."
    "我沒有提她沒有雙腿卻有這樣的表現是多麼令人佩服。我想她自己已經知道了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3650
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_edfe4477:

    # "Besides, it seems like it would take away from her efforts, somehow."
    "而且，那樣說似乎反而會削弱她努力的價值。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3656
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_6e7e5131:

    # emi "Great to hear! I was worried that I looked a little slow on the relay, but I guess I did fine, huh?"
    emi "太好了！我還擔心我在接力賽上看起來有點慢，但我想我表現得還不錯，對吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3661
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_c997b75e:

    # hi "Actually, I noticed—{w=.4}{nw}"
    hi "其實，我注意到——{w=.4}{nw}"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3668
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_fe1e4a5e:

    # "Rin kicks me and keeps me from finishing my sentence."
    "琳踢了我一下，讓我沒能把話說完。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3673
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_d5845e4d:

    # emi "What was that all about?"
    emi "什麼？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3678
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_27bbeb35:

    # rin "He noticed it. At the end."
    rin "他注意到了。在最後。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3683
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_0ed1fabc:

    # emi "Hmm, that's no good."
    emi "嗯，那可不太好。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3688
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_c64d3b7a:

    # emi "Guess the nurse will look at it for me later."
    emi "看來晚點要請校醫幫我看看了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3696
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_321792a3:

    # "There's a carelessness in her voice, as if it isn't a big deal, but I suddenly notice a slight twitch on her face."
    "她的語氣很隨意，好像這不是什麼大事，但我突然注意到她臉上輕微地抽動了一下。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3698
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_8eda6a0e:

    # "Like she's trying to hide the fact that she's in pain."
    "就像是她在刻意隱瞞哪裡的痛楚一樣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3700
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_d231356b:

    # "It's then that I notice her breathing is a little shallow, too."
    "這時我才注意到，她的呼吸也有點急促。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3702
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_b16f343b:

    # "I guess she really is hurt."
    "看來她真的是受傷了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3704
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_8fb5a030:

    # "She must notice my concern, because she skips up to me and gives me a friendly pat on the shoulder."
    "她一定注意到了我的關心，因為她跳到我面前，友好地拍了拍我的肩膀。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3710
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_c23c81e3:

    # emi "Hey, you look a little worried!"
    emi "嘿，你看起來有點擔心喔！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3715
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_21e25a75:

    # emi "I'm fine, really!"
    emi "我沒事，真的！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3717
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_1fe2c3ba:

    # emi "Just sore from all the running, is all."
    emi "只是跑了這麼多，肌肉痠痛而已。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3722
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_8aeee8eb:

    # emi "And come on, a little pain isn't going to stop me."
    emi "而且拜託，一點點痛是阻止不了我的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3724
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_3012bc85:

    # hi "Oh no?"
    hi "喔，是嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3729
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_d2836be6:

    # "Emi grins, and for a moment she looks like she did during her sprint, fierce and unconquerable."
    "笑美咧嘴一笑，有那麼一瞬間，她看起來就像衝刺時那樣，充滿鬥志、無人能敵。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3731
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_7a0ce800:

    # "Or to put it another way, really beautiful."
    "或者換句話說，真的很漂亮。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3736
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_07790361:

    # emi "Hasn't yet."
    emi "還沒有過。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3738
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_ae771e14:

    # hi "Well then. I guess I shouldn't worry, huh?"
    hi "嗯，那麼。我想我不用擔心了，對吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3743
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_7abf794a:

    # emi "Damn right! I'm Emi Ibarazaki, fastest thing on no legs! I don't stop for anything!"
    emi "沒錯！我是茨崎笑美，最快的無腿生物！我不會為任何東西而停下腳步的！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3745
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_05823cbc:

    # hi "Impressive."
    hi "真了不起。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3750
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_a4decc24:

    # "Emi giggles, and then seems to remember something."
    "笑美咯咯地笑了笑，然後像是突然想起來了什麼。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3755
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_eb68f3c3:

    # emi "Oh, before I forget…"
    emi "喔，在我忘記之前……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3757
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_c8698477:

    # emi "Rin and I are going to do something next Sunday as a post-track meet celebration!"
    emi "琳和我想在下週日辦個田徑賽後的慶祝活動！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3762
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_6fe2177a:

    # emi "You should come along!"
    emi "你也一起來吧！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3767
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_97fc141d:

    # emi "Normally we do it the day after, but since the track meet was on a Sunday, I've got homework and class and all that stuff to take care of."
    emi "通常我們第二天就會慶祝，但因為這次的比賽是在週日舉行的，而我明天還有作業和課。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3772
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_17ce21d4:

    # emi "Plus our morning run, of course."
    emi "當然，還有我們的晨跑。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3774
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_e6d98932:

    # hi "Right, of course."
    hi "嗯，沒錯。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3776
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_ce333f72:

    # hi "Oh, right. Your mom wanted to say she's proud of you."
    hi "喔，對了。妳媽媽想說她為妳感到驕傲。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3778
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_586c46c7:

    # hi "She'll call you later tonight."
    hi "她今天晚點會打電話給妳。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3783
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_6b87640b:

    # emi "I thought I saw her in the stands!"
    emi "我就想說在看台上好像看到她了！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3788
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_169ce240:

    # emi "I'm glad she made it!"
    emi "她能來真是太好了！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3793
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_ae6b1c2b:

    # emi "Used to be my dad who showed up to my meets, but Mom's done a pretty good job of taking over."
    emi "以前都是我爸來看我的比賽，不過媽媽接手後也做得很好。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3799
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_752c6e25:

    # "She shivers slightly, and I realize that she's still all sweaty."
    "她輕輕地顫抖了一下，我才意識到她還滿身是汗。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3801
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_8fc3cff3:

    # "A breeze has started to blow, too."
    "也開始起風了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3803
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_815488d2:

    # "I'm not cold at all, and I've got my jacket with me, so without a word I throw it around her shoulders."
    "我一點也不冷，而且我帶著夾克，於是我二話不說地把它披在她肩上。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3815
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_4ef47458:

    # "Emi jumps slightly and then grins at me."
    "笑美稍微跳了一下，然後對我咧嘴一笑。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3820
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_9ab1c330:

    # emi "Hey, thanks!"
    emi "嘿，謝啦！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3825
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_e688ef3d:

    # emi "It's getting a little cold, I guess."
    emi "我想是變得有點冷了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3827
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_38e88afc:

    # hi "Yeah, looked like it."
    hi "嗯，看起來是。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3829
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_328b4b99:

    # "Just as I begin to wonder whether or not giving Emi my jacket could be taken the wrong way, a boy in a track uniform approaches."
    "正當我開始思考把夾克給笑美會不會被誤會時，一個穿著田徑服的男孩走了過來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3831
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_46dd8a0c:

    # "Teammate" "Hey, Emi! You're going to miss the medal ceremony!"
    "田徑隊員" "喂！笑美！妳要錯過頒獎典禮了！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3836
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_8388fbc4:

    # emi "Oh yeah, thanks!"
    emi "喔對，謝啦！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3842
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_617381f4:

    # "She turns to Rin and myself."
    "她轉向我和琳。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3844
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_ee4af1d4:

    # emi "You don't have to stick around for this part. It takes forever."
    emi "你們不用留下來等這個。這要花很久。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3849
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_a870e1be:

    # emi "Besides, you should get cracking on your homework now if you don't want to be up late, Hisao."
    emi "而且，久夫，如果你不想熬夜的話，現在就該開始做作業了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3854
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_8c433706:

    # emi "Morning run tomorrow! Don't forget!"
    emi "明天晨跑！別忘了！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3859
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_6e315c48:

    # hi "How could I?"
    hi "我怎麼可能忘？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3865
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_d979fc34:

    # emi "Good point. I mean, it's spending time with {b}me{/b}, after all."
    emi "說得也是。畢竟，那可是跟{b}我{/b}在一起的時間呢。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3881
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_9ed08ccb:

    # "With this, she waves quickly and dashes off to receive her medals, or whatever they pass off as a medal these days."
    "說完，她迅速地揮了揮手，跑去領她的獎牌，或者不管現在都用什麼東西來代替獎牌。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3890
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_18d0c56c:

    # "Rin and I head away from the track, Rin remaining deep in whatever thoughts she has for most of the walk back to her dorm."
    "我和琳離開了操場，在走回她宿舍的大部分路上，琳都沉浸在她自己的思緒中。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3892
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_18abd5bd:

    # "As I see her off, she speaks up."
    "在我送她離開時，她開口了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3897
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_4307978d:

    # rin "You're probably not getting that coat back, I think."
    rin "我想，你那件外套大概拿不回來了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3899
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_eaa0c1dd:

    # hi "I'm sure I'll get it back eventually."
    hi "我相信我總有一天會拿回來的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3904
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_ef346eb2:

    # rin "Interesting. Take it as it comes, huh?"
    rin "真有趣。順其自然，是嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3909
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_46b8ecfa:

    # rin "Very Emi-ish."
    rin "非常有笑美的風格。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3914
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_c4e39d47:

    # "With this odd statement, she turns and heads into the building."
    "說完這句奇怪的話，她轉身走進了大樓。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3916
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_480b1e32:

    # "Honestly, was it that big a deal?"
    "老實說，有那麼嚴重嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3918
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_0a363d04:

    # "Emi was cold and, unless I'm mistaken, in pain."
    "笑美覺得冷，而且，如果我沒看錯的話，她還在痛。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3920
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_83ed3073:

    # "Giving her a solution to at least one of those problems seems like an obvious reaction."
    "至少幫她解決其中一個問題，這似乎是很自然的反應。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3922
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_31bcb3e8:

    # "Though I guess there is a chance I could lose my jacket if Emi never remembers to return it."
    "不過，如果笑美一直不記得還，我確實有可能會失去我的夾克。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3924
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_6f55c046:

    # "I guess Rin has a point."
    "我想琳說的也有道理。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3926
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_25f6be0c:

    # "Still, I can't bring myself to muster much worry over the whole thing."
    "不過，我還是沒辦法為這整件事太過擔心。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3928
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_8ef060f3:

    # "After all, it's been getting warmer lately."
    "畢竟，最近天氣越來越暖和了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3930
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_c5518592:

    # "I don't need a jacket."
    "我不需要夾克。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3932
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_bd9ef064:

    # "Odd. I think I used to be a little more responsible with my stuff."
    "……怪了，我記得我以前要更愛惜自己的東西啊。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3934
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_be4dc657:

    # "'Emi-ish,' huh?"
    "「有笑美的風格」，嗯？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3936
translate zh_hant a2_emi_track_meeting_ae06e3a1:

    # "Maybe that's not really a bad thing."
    "也許那也不是什麼壞事。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3953
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_9104cbd5:

    # nk "You haven't been forgetting to take your medicine, have you?"
    nk "你沒有忘記吃藥吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3957
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_04e0a452:

    # nk "I'm catching a little murmur."
    nk "我聽到了一點雜音。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3959
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_4ef53a0f:

    # nk "You should take it easy for a few days."
    nk "你這幾天應該要好好休息。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3961
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_cc7ec62e:

    # "The nurse's words hurt me far more than the exhaustion of the morning run ever could."
    "校醫的話比晨跑的疲憊感更讓我難受。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3963
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_bc525df4:

    # "Take it easy for a few days?"
    "這幾天好好休息？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3965
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_c2e246e1:

    # "I knew I should have kept quiet."
    "我就知道我不該多嘴。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3967
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_ca97ba80:

    # "I keep my eyes on the floor, feeling like a complete idiot."
    "我盯著地板，感覺自己像個十足的白痴。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3969
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_3601906c:

    # "Of course I hadn't been remembering to take my medicine."
    "我當然不記得吃藥了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3971
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_d62c8b16:

    # "I've been rushing out of my room to get to the track before Emi."
    "我每天都急著衝出房間，想在笑美之前到操場。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3973
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_52afa160:

    # "After the track meet a few days ago, I felt… inspired."
    "幾天前的田徑賽後，我感覺……受到了鼓舞。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3975
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_75f36723:

    # "So I've been running warm-up laps in the morning before Emi shows up."
    "所以我每天早上在笑美出現前，都會先跑幾圈熱身。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3977
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_bcd24ee9:

    # "But then today while she and I were running, I felt a little pain in my chest."
    "但今天，當我和她一起跑步時，我感覺胸口有點痛。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3979
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_629e03df:

    # "It was only slight, and it was only for a second, so I mentioned it to the nurse."
    "只是輕微的痛，而且只有一下下，所以我跟校醫提了一下。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3981
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_55263bda:

    # hi "Honestly, it wasn't that bad."
    hi "說真的，沒有你想像的那麼嚴重。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3983
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_1840490b:

    # hi "I mean I kept running and finished just fine, so really it couldn't have been that bad…"
    hi "我的意思是，我還是繼續跑，而且順利跑完了，所以真的不可能那麼嚴重……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3985
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_69dde4aa:

    # "Why do I feel like I'm making excuses to the nurse?"
    "為什麼我覺得我像在跟校醫找藉口？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3987
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_b632acc6:

    # "Moreover, why do I feel a need to justify continuing to run despite the pain?"
    "而且，為什麼我覺得有必要為自己忍痛繼續跑這件事辯解？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3989
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_97ba49af:

    # "Really, it comes down to my being unwilling to concern Emi, who seemed concerned anyway."
    "說真的，歸根究柢，是我不想讓笑美擔心，儘管她看起來還是很擔心。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3991
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_989bd887:

    # "I'm not sure how she was able to tell there was anything wrong, but she claims I stumbled a little."
    "我不確定她怎麼看得出有問題，但她說我踉蹌了一下。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3993
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_d89655cb:

    # "She's the one who insisted I tell the nurse, so now I feel bad for worrying her at all."
    "是她堅持要我告訴校醫的，所以現在我覺得很抱歉讓她擔心。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3995
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_555fa8d9:

    # "The nurse is shaking his head ruefully while Emi paces outside the room."
    "校醫懊惱地搖著頭，而笑美在房間外來回踱步。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3997
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_ed5127e7:

    # nk "Hisao, I know it's difficult for you get into a new routine, but if you don't want to find yourself in a lot of trouble you're going to have to try harder."
    nk "久夫，我知道要你適應新的生活很困難，但如果你不想惹上大麻煩，就得更努力一點。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3999
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_74a58e8f:

    # nk "You can't afford to forget your pills, and you can't push yourself too hard."
    nk "你不能忘記吃藥，也不能把自己逼得太緊。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4001
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_6dcbe05c:

    # hi "But if I don't push myself, how will I improve?"
    hi "但如果我不逼自己，我要怎麼進步？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4003
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_ab68091c:

    # "I don't know where that came from."
    "我不知道這句話是從哪冒出來的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4005
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_dd54f9de:

    # "The nurse seems to have an idea."
    "但校醫似乎知道怎麼回應我。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4010
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_7b44c03f:

    # nk "Now where have I heard that before?"
    nk "我以前在哪聽過這句話呢？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4015
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_fb56c34d:

    # "He laughs and pats me on the shoulder."
    "他笑了笑，拍了拍我的肩膀。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4017
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_e01c0d22:

    # nk "Ha! She's rubbing off on you, I guess."
    nk "哈！看來你被她影響了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4022
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_54a3ec30:

    # "His expression changes again, and he's back in serious mode."
    "他的表情又變了，回到了嚴肅的模式。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4024
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_8c820eb4:

    # nk "Look, I'm not saying you shouldn't push yourself."
    nk "聽著，我不是說你不該逼自己。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4026
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_8a0de978:

    # nk "But that doesn't mean you shouldn't be taking your medication, and it doesn't mean you shouldn't stop if your chest starts to bother you."
    nk "但那不代表你可以不吃藥，也不代表你胸口不舒服的時候可以不停下來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4028
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_53b086a9:

    # nk "I'd prefer not to have any fatalities while I'm on staff here."
    nk "在我任職期間，我可不希望出任何人命。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4033
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_a2bbdfdc:

    # nk "A bit of a lofty goal, to be sure, but I'm always up for a challenge."
    nk "這目標確實有點遠大，但我隨時準備好接受挑戰。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4035
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_5b504b3f:

    # "I hate to admit it, but I think he's right."
    "雖然不願意承認，但我想他是對的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4037
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_f3c98e89:

    # "I've got to remember to take my medication."
    "我得要記著按時吃藥。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4039
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_5627077e:

    # hi "You're right. I'm sorry to worry you."
    hi "你說得對。抱歉讓你擔心了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4044
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_8470a8fd:

    # nk "Who's worried? You're a smart kid, right?"
    nk "誰擔心了？你是個聰明的孩子，對吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4049
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_75179be3:

    # nk "I know you can be responsible, Hisao. A situation like yours, you've got to learn to be responsible fast."
    nk "我知道你可以負責任的，久夫。像你這種情況，你必須很快學會負責任。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4051
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_ee322606:

    # hi "I know, I know."
    hi "我知道，我知道。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4053
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_b47407ec:

    # "His expression suddenly becomes devious."
    "他然後露出了十分狡猾的表情。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4058
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_3967fe8b:

    # nk "I suppose you've started to enjoy your runs with Emi then, eh?"
    nk "我想你已經開始享受和笑美一起跑步了吧，嗯？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4060
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_13f3cfa2:

    # hi "Yeah, they've really been helping me."
    hi "是啊，那真的對我很有幫助。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4062
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_ec081ade:

    # hi "I mean, until today I was feeling a lot more healthy."
    hi "我的意思是，直到今天為止，我都覺得自己健康多了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4064
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_b8385b1f:

    # hi "Plus it's really impressive to see Emi run. Did you see her at the track meet?"
    hi "而且看笑美跑步真的很讓人佩服。你去看了她的田徑賽了嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4066
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_3bbc9230:

    # hi "She was incredible!"
    hi "她太厲害了！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4071
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_9efda7cf:

    # "The nurse nods, grinning all the while."
    "校醫一邊點頭，一邊咧嘴微笑。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4073
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_8d3968e3:

    # nk "That she was, Hisao. I watched her first couple of races before I had some business to take care of, but she told me all about it."
    nk "她當然厲害，久夫。我看了她開頭的幾個項目，但之後有事就先離開了，但她後來也把之後的事情跟我說了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4078
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_ceb25c6d:

    # nk "Kind of you to loan her your jacket, by the way."
    nk "啊順帶一提，多謝你，將你的夾克借給她了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4080
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_6b622be4:

    # hi "Huh? Oh yeah, it wasn't that big of a deal."
    hi "嗯？喔，對啊，那沒什麼大不了的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4082
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_bd199f72:

    # "I had honestly forgotten all about that. I still haven't gotten it back."
    "我老實說已經完全忘了那件事。我到現在還沒拿回來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4087
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_a1b64653:

    # "The nurse gets a smile that makes me feel like he's just made a joke."
    "校醫朝我笑了笑，我覺得他剛才只是在和我開玩笑而已。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4089
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_e38d4d06:

    # nk "Not to you, but Emi certainly appreciated it."
    nk "對你來說可能不算啥，但笑美真的很感激哦。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4091
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_14f47bce:

    # nk "And I know she appreciates your running with her in the mornings."
    nk "而且我知道她很感激你早上陪她跑步。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4093
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_9936d3ce:

    # "This one catches me off guard a little. Sure, she mentioned that it's easier to keep to a schedule with an extra person, but I didn't think that I was doing her a favor at all."
    "這句話讓我有點措手不及。當然，她提過多一個人比較容易遵守時間表，但我從不覺得我是在幫她。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4095
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_bb36e31a:

    # hi "I thought she was doing me the favor of helping me follow the doctor's orders."
    hi "我一直都覺得她是在你的委託下才來幫我的忙的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4097
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_e7eed434:

    # nk "She tries harder when you're around."
    nk "有你在的時候，她會更努力。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4099
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_135da16b:

    # nk "If there's someone else running with her, she's going to push herself more."
    nk "如果有人和她在一起，她會盡可能的加油。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4101
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_94bde393:

    # nk "And she tries even harder when you're around because, well, it's you."
    nk "而且有你在的時候，她會更加努力，因為……嗯，因為是你啊。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4103
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_0573a0ef:

    # hi "What the heck does that mean?"
    hi "這到底是什麼意思？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4108
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_a5f484c5:

    # nk "Oh ho, you'd love to know, wouldn't you?"
    nk "喔嗬，你很想知道吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4110
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_b4565309:

    # "He laughs in the style of evil megalomaniacs."
    "他笑得像個邪惡的自大狂。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4115
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_1bbeeebc:

    # nk "No seriously, it's because you're her friend."
    nk "不，說真的，因為你是她的朋友。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4117
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_6a51db97:

    # nk "If Rin ran with her, I'm sure she'd do the same."
    nk "如果琳跟她一起跑，我相信她也會一樣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4119
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_c86c45c2:

    # nk "Well, probably."
    nk "嗯，大概吧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4121
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_d714ac6d:

    # nk "But that's not the point."
    nk "但那不是重點。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4123
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_93c99ff8:

    # nk "The point is, you're helping her, even if you don't know you are."
    nk "重點是，你在幫助她，即使你不知道。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4128
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_6597290a:

    # nk "And she's grateful for that, even if she never says it."
    nk "而她對此心存感激，即使她從未說出口。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4130
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_c655ed4a:

    # hi "What do you mean 'even if she never says it?'"
    hi "你說「即使她從未說出口」是什麼意思？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4135
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_a4585d71:

    # nk "Emi doesn't talk a lot, but she and I have known each other long enough that I can read her most of the time."
    nk "笑美話不多，但我和她認識夠久了，大部分時候我都能讀懂她的心思。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4137
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_d7df0e2b:

    # "I'll admit it. I have no idea what he's talking about."
    "我承認。我完全不知道他在說什麼。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4139
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_e8fb71f6:

    # "Emi always seems pretty talkative to me."
    "對我來說，笑美一直都很健談。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4141
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_e1f8a5e6:

    # hi "I see."
    hi "我明白了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4143
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_3454e207:

    # "The nurse suddenly realizes that he's been rambling and stops talking, looking a little embarrassed."
    "校醫突然意識到自己一直在滔滔不絕，便停了下來，看起來有點尷尬。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4148
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_1ba20d76:

    # nk "Anyway, you don't have to stop your morning exercise."
    nk "總之，你不用停止早上的運動。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4153
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_8bbfca7b:

    # nk "Just walk the track instead of running for a few days. Let things calm down."
    nk "這幾天就改成在操場走路代替跑步。讓身體緩和一下。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4158
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_37c57c4d:

    # nk "And take your damned medicine!"
    nk "還有，給我乖乖吃藥！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4169
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_53bfda73:

    # "I laugh as I exit the office, bumping straight into Emi."
    "我笑著走出辦公室，直接撞上了笑美。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4174
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_b27eb373:

    # hi "Whoops, sorry about that."
    hi "哎呀，抱歉。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4179
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_653e5cbb:

    # emi "Are you okay? What did the nurse say?"
    emi "你還好嗎？校醫怎麼說？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4181
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_438a8b00:

    # emi "Do you need to go to a hospital?"
    emi "你需要去醫院嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4186
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_be0288f3:

    # emi "Omigosh, it was my fault, wasn't it?"
    emi "天啊，是我的錯，對不對？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4191
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_18a403ca:

    # emi "I've been pushing you too hard, haven't I?"
    emi "我把你逼得太緊了，是不是？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4196
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_01c6ca24:

    # emi "I'm a horrible person!"
    emi "我真是個糟糕的人啊！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4198
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_1e191e33:

    # "The words pour forth like a torrent. She's really agitated."
    "她看起來很是焦急，一口氣嘰裡呱啦地說道。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4200
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_41f7398a:

    # "I didn't expect her to be this concerned about me, to be honest."
    "老實說，我沒想到她會這麼擔心我。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4202
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_afba2b32:

    # "Gotta calm her down… but how the hell do I do that?"
    "得讓她冷靜下來……但我到底該怎麼做？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4204
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_1359bd2e:

    # "I do the only thing I can think of."
    "我做了我唯一能想到的事。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4211
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_2f436cc1:

    # "I give her a hug. Emi tenses up slightly, so I pat her head in what I hope is a reassuring manner."
    "我給了她一個擁抱。笑美身體稍微僵硬了一下，於是我用我希望是安撫的方式拍了拍她的頭。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4213
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_1466070d:

    # hi "Hey, settle down!"
    hi "嘿，冷靜點！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4215
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_0271060d:

    # hi "I'm fine, okay? No worries."
    hi "我沒事，好嗎？別擔心。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4220
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_66746f83:

    # "I can feel Emi's body relax as I continue to assure her I'm fine."
    "在我不斷向她保證我沒事時，我能感覺到笑美的身體放鬆了下來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4222
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_1ce8dd6a:

    # "Her arms wrap around me, as if she's trying to confirm that I'm not about to fall over dead."
    "她的手臂環繞著我，彷彿在確認我不會突然倒地死去。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4224
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_58534f08:

    # "I catch a whiff of her hair. It smells like sweat, or how adrenaline should smell. It's the scent of activity."
    "我聞到一股她頭髮的氣味。聞起來像汗水，或者說是腎上腺素該有的味道。那是活力的氣息。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4226
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_d8674e3e:

    # "And a hint of strawberries. From her shampoo, I suspect."
    "還有一絲草莓味。我猜是她的洗髮精。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4228
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_26227128:

    # hi "I just need to remember to take my medicine, that's all."
    hi "我只需要記得吃藥，就這樣而已。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4230
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_2b4b4f59:

    # hi "Don't worry about it. It's not your fault."
    hi "別擔心。不是妳的錯。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4235
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_f0ded6da:

    # emi "You're sure?"
    emi "你確定？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4237
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_4995338e:

    # "Her voice is muffled, mostly because at the moment her face is pressed into my chest."
    "她的聲音悶悶的，大概是因為她的臉正埋在我的胸口的緣故吧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4239
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_4bdfaf88:

    # hi "Yeah, I'm sure. I just need to take it a little easy for the next few days."
    hi "啊，我很確定。我只需要接下來的幾天放鬆一下就行了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4241
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_eb6c9745:

    # "It suddenly occurs to me how close the two of us are."
    "我突然意識到我們兩人的距離有多麼的近。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4243
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_0459db22:

    # "It also occurs to me how nice being this close feels."
    "我也意識到，這麼親近的感覺有多好。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4245
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_fc98512b:

    # "I can feel Emi's heartbeat calming down, and I have to resist the urge to rest my chin on the top of her head."
    "我能感覺到笑美的心跳平靜下來，而我必須克制住想把下巴靠在她頭頂的衝動。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4250
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_084f4f83:

    # emi "Thank goodness."
    emi "謝天謝地。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4252
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_8d14fb63:

    # emi "You really had me worried there, Hisao."
    emi "你真的讓我擔心死了，久夫。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4266
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_ed72ff73:

    # nk "Emi, you going to come in here any time soon?"
    nk "笑美，妳到底要不要進來啊？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4271
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_4ab70111:

    # nk "…Oh, I'm sorry. Was I interrupting?"
    nk "……喔，抱歉。我打擾到你們了嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4276
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_3a0ed190:

    # "The two of us spring apart as if the other just caught on fire."
    "我們兩人像是對方身上著了火一樣，猛地分開。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4281
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_f3c8eec3:

    # "Emi brushes her hair back nervously and laughs."
    "笑美緊張地把頭髮撥到後面，尷尬地笑了笑。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4285
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_a089010a:

    # emi "'Course not!"
    emi "當、當然沒有！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4291
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_ff3df2ea:

    # emi "I'll uh… see you later, okay?"
    emi "我呃……晚點見，好嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4296
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_23e95fc3:

    # emi "Oh, and Hisao?"
    emi "喔，還有，久夫？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4298
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_34d1d59d:

    # hi "Hmm?"
    hi "嗯？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4305
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_7f390212:

    # emi "Take your damn medicine!"
    emi "別給我忘記吃藥！！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4307
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_2be57438:

    # "This last phrase is punctuated by a punch to the shoulder."
    "最後一個字，她用給我肩膀一記鐵拳來強調。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4309
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_575088d7:

    # hi "Yeah, yeah, I'll remember."
    hi "好啦，好啦，我會記得。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4311
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_181ad1e9:

    # hi "See you later."
    hi "晚點見。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4316
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_4a91de78:

    # "The nurse smiles again like he's in on some joke I don't know about and waves to me as I head for my room, feeling a burning in my cheeks."
    "校醫又笑了，好像他知道什麼我不知道的笑話似的，在我離開時對我揮了揮手，走向房間時我感覺臉頰發燙。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4323
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_9a837167:

    # "I need a shower."
    "我需要沖個澡。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4325
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_521a602d:

    # "A cold one, if the thoughts running through my head now are any indication."
    "如果指標是我我腦中的東西的話，那得是個冷水澡。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4327
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_c032d237:

    # "She was really soft."
    "她感覺起來真的很軟。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4329
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_fb09b9d8:

    # "My pills are waiting for me when I make it to my room."
    "回到房間時，我的藥正等著我。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4331
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_03dc3717:

    # "I swallow them without a second thought."
    "我想都沒想就把它們吞了下去。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4333
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_4f652f18:

    # "I don't know why I didn't think of waiting until after the runs to take them. For some reason I figured it was when I woke up or not at all."
    "我不知道為什麼我沒想到跑完步後也可以吃。不知為何，我一直以為要嘛是起床時吃，要嘛就乾脆不吃。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4335
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_f5fcd898:

    # "But no, they only need to be taken every twenty-four hours. The exact time of day doesn't factor into it."
    "但不對，它們只需要每二十四小時服用一次。一天中的確切時間並不重要。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4337
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_5cda4671:

    # "My thoughts drift back to the hug in the hallway."
    "我的思緒飄回了走廊上的那個擁抱。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4339
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_61574813:

    # "It's weird, you'd expect someone to smell foul after a run, but for some reason, Emi smelled… right. That tinge of sweat just seemed to fit her."
    "很奇怪，你會以為跑完步的人聞起來會很難聞，但不知為何，笑美的味道……恰到好處。那淡淡的汗味似乎很適合她。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4341
translate zh_hant a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_19b1712b:

    # "I really need that shower."
    "我真的需要去沖個澡了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4355
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4362
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_f7b64135:

    # n "{vspace=60}Strange that it feels so natural for me to go up to the roof these days."
    n "{vspace=60}說也奇怪，最近我到屋頂去，感覺是那麼地自然。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4364
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_cb2c2824:

    # n "I never would have done such a thing at my old school."
    n "在我以前的學校，我絕對不會做這種事。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4366
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_b3d554b3:

    # n "In those days I liked to eat alone… no, that's not quite true. Though I liked to sit alone, I also liked to watch people."
    n "那時候我喜歡一個人吃飯……不，這麼說也不太對。雖然我喜歡獨自坐著，但我也喜歡觀察人群。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4368
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_9fe8a6a0:

    # n "I always figured that was the sort of person I was, but it appears I was wrong."
    n "我一直以為我就是那種人，但看來我錯了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4370
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_514577fb:

    # n "Then again, I also thought I was the sort of person who had a normal heart, so there you have it."
    n "話說回來，我也曾以為我是那種心臟正常的人，一樣的道理。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4372
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_7ca1d29e:

    # n "I don't know myself that well."
    n "我其實不怎麼了解自己。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4374
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_a499e48e:

    # n "Now I'm on the roof so that I can have lunch with a couple of people."
    n "現在我會上屋頂，是為了跟人一起吃午餐。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4376
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_93a175f0:

    # n "And they are both girls, which is even stranger."
    n "而且她們都是女生，這就更奇怪了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4378
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_e9809d54:

    # n "Oddly enough, I feel closer to Emi and Rin than I felt to anyone at my old school."
    n "說來也怪，我覺得跟笑美和琳的距離，比跟我以前學校的任何人都還要親近。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4380
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_e90c2efe:

    # n "Somehow I get the feeling they'd at least visit me if I wound up in the hospital."
    n "不知為何，我有種感覺，要是我又住院了，她們至少會來探望我。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4386
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_c56552b8:

    # nvl clear
    # "I focus on the view from the roof, banishing such thoughts from my head."
    nvl clear
    "我專注於屋頂上的景色，把這些念頭從腦海中驅逐出去。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4390
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_8b812c17:

    # "There's a light breeze blowing, and the sun is shining high in the sky."
    "微風輕拂，陽光高掛天空。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4392
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_af9c0e66:

    # "The sky itself is a deep blue, with hardly a cloud in it. It's gotten pleasantly warm, and as I sit down to wait for my friends, I close my eyes and enjoy the feeling of the sun seeping into my skin."
    "天空本身是深藍色的，幾乎沒有一絲雲彩。天氣變得宜人溫暖，坐著等朋友們的時候，我閉上眼睛，享受陽光滲入皮膚的感覺。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4401
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_dc590c55:

    # "Voices intrude upon the edge of hearing."
    "聲音闖入了我的聽力的邊緣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4403
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_eecf29ae:

    # emi "—seems to have fallen asleep on us, Rin."
    emi "——看來他睡著了呢，琳。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4405
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_796495d9:

    # rin "Maybe he's faking, to lull us into a false sense of security."
    rin "也許他在裝睡，想讓我們鬆懈戒心。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4407
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_d4fa74d3:

    # emi "Why would he do that?"
    emi "他為什麼要這麼做？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4409
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_c7cccc3e:

    # rin "No idea."
    rin "不知道。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4411
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_3eb64127:

    # emi "Still, you make a good point."
    emi "不過，妳說得有道理。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4413
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_4eb65cc0:

    # emi "We should kick him or something to make sure he's really asleep."
    emi "我們應該踢他一下之類的，確認他是不是真的睡著了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4417
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_867ff869:

    # hi "Huh? What?"
    hi "呃？什麼？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4428
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_631a6ecb:

    # "Emi looms over me like only a short girl can, peering at me intently."
    "笑美以她那嬌小身材專門的方式從上方俯視著我。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4433
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_1b92be72:

    # emi "Oh, you're awake. I guess we don't have to kick you then."
    emi "哦，你醒啦。那看來我們就不用踢你了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4438
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_20b9aa48:

    # rin "Was it part of your master plan?"
    rin "這是你大計畫的一部分嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4440
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_c2ca05ef:

    # hi "What are you talking about?"
    hi "妳們在說什麼啊？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4445
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_6c58244c:

    # "Emi shrugs, her twin tails bouncing with the motion."
    "笑美聳了聳肩，雙馬尾隨著她的動作前後擺動。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4450
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_1ba98fac:

    # emi "I'm not sure either."
    emi "我也不太確定。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4455
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_81fdf20b:

    # emi "You must be pretty tired to fall asleep out here."
    emi "你居然能在這裡睡著，一定很累吧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4460
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_451802f1:

    # emi "Although it's pretty comfortable, I suppose."
    emi "不過我想，這裡還挺舒服的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4467
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_c3460221:

    # "She plops down next to me and begins to eat."
    "她一屁股坐在我旁邊，開始吃東西。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4476
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_607c0507:

    # "Rin sits opposite from the two of us, a move which only makes me more aware of the girl sitting next to me."
    "琳坐在我們兩個的對面，這個舉動只讓我更加意識到坐在我身旁的女孩。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4478
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_f4a09856:

    # "If I didn't know any better, I'd swear Rin did it on purpose."
    "如果我對琳不夠了解，我會發誓她是故意的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4480
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_d679e94f:

    # "I concentrate on my food, trying to tune out the majority of the conversation that Rin and Emi are having."
    "我專心吃我的食物，試圖忽略琳和笑美之間大部分的對話。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4482
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_45636406:

    # "Despite my best efforts, however, I still find myself glancing over at Emi whenever she speaks."
    "然而，儘管我盡了最大的努力，每當笑美說話時，我還是會忍不住瞥向她。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4487
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_373deafb:

    # "I notice how she purses her lips when she's thinking about something, squinting slightly as if that would improve her thinking ability."
    "我注意到她在思考時會噘起嘴唇，微微瞇起眼睛，彷彿那樣能提升她的思考能力。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4495
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_538269a9:

    # "Rin says something that makes Emi laugh, and I notice, perhaps for the first time, how she laughs with her whole body, rocking back and forth, head thrown back, almost like she's about to fall over."
    "琳說了些什麼讓笑美笑了起來，而我，或許是第一次，注意到她是用全身在笑，身體前後搖晃，頭向後仰，幾乎像是快要跌倒一樣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4497
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_98b5e433:

    # "I probably look like a creep."
    "……我這麼目不轉睛地盯著她看一定很像個變態吧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4502
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_12a44107:

    # "It's about this time that I realize Emi's looking at me. Her voice raised slightly, so she's probably just asked me a question."
    "就在這時，我意識到笑美在看著我。她的聲音稍微提高了一些，所以她可能剛問了我一個問題。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4504
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_dee1e459:

    # hi "Huh? Sorry, I kinda zoned out for a moment there."
    hi "嗯？抱歉，我剛剛有點恍神。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4510
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_364ba3fb:

    # "Emi rolls her eyes, while a slight quirk of the eyebrow is the only sign that Rin's even paying attention."
    "笑美翻了個白眼，而琳只是眉毛微微一挑，她唯一表示有在注意聽的跡象。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4512
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_58a3156e:

    # emi "I said, did you get a career survey in your class too?"
    emi "我說，你們班也收到生涯調查表了嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4517
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_ccb305ed:

    # emi "You know, one of those 'What do you want to do after high school?' things?"
    emi "就是那種「高中畢業後想做什麼？」的東西？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4519
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_4ca28fb9:

    # hi "I don't… think so. Maybe we'll get one tomorrow."
    hi "我……不這麼認為。也許我們明天會拿到。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4524
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_d7989ed2:

    # emi "What are you going to put down?"
    emi "你打算填什麼？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4526
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_a65c22a3:

    # "That's a really good question."
    "這真是個好問題。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4528
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_ce5a4d8c:

    # "I guess I always figured I'd go to college after high school, but I've no idea what I'd do once I got there."
    "我想我一直都覺得高中畢業後會上大學，但我完全不知道到了那裡要做什麼。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4530
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_06a6ff19:

    # "And with the heart attack and all, I'd really been concentrating on each day as it came rather than making long-term plans."
    "而且因為心臟病發作什麼的，我真的都只專注於過好每一天，而不是做長遠的計畫。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4532
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_4ebe5fec:

    # "I suppose I can safely start planning ahead, again."
    "我想我現在又可以放心地開始規劃未來了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4534
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_7ec08c9f:

    # "I've always liked having at least a vague plan for my future, so it'll be nice to come up with one again."
    "我一直都喜歡對未來至少有個模糊的方向，所以能再想想也很不錯。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4536
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_dda18824:

    # "Of course, that doesn't change the fact that right now I've got absolutely…"
    "當然，那並不能改變我現在完全……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4538
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_931afad5:

    # hi "…No clue."
    hi "……毫無頭緒。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4540
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_208036a4:

    # hi "I always kind of assumed I'd figure it out in college. That or just become a salaryman. That's pretty popular."
    hi "我總覺得上了大學自然就會想通了。再不然就是當個上班族。大多人是這樣吧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4542
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_efe071c2:

    # "But do I really want to? That's a tough question."
    "但我真的想這樣嗎？這是個很難的問題。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4544
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_97ac566c:

    # "I guess I don't really want to do anything."
    "我想我其實什麼都不想做吧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4549
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_941e9a7e:

    # emi "You don't sound very excited about that one, do you?"
    emi "你聽起來對那樣不怎麼感興趣，對吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4553
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_a639bfab:

    # "She laughs as she says this, and I'm caught up in her laugh again."
    "她邊說邊笑，我又再次被她的笑聲吸引。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4555
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_9dbf7785:

    # "It's so… girlish. High and giggly, like a… well, pardon the cliché - like a babbling brook."
    "那笑聲……很有女孩子氣。高亢清脆，就像……嗯，請原諒這個老調的比喻——就像潺潺的小溪。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4557
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_7667166f:

    # "It bubbles out of her, starting in her belly and working its way up her throat."
    "聲音從她腹部開始，順著她的喉嚨從她嘴上的笑容中流出。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4559
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_c6bc4755:

    # "I can't help but laugh myself - it's infectious."
    "我忍不住也笑了起來——那笑聲太有感染力了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4561
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_0e80b5f2:

    # hi "Yeah, I guess I'm pretty unhappy with the salaryman idea."
    hi "對啊，我是不怎麼想當上班族。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4563
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_d209318d:

    # hi "But to be honest, I haven't given much thought to the future recently."
    hi "但老實說，我最近沒怎麼思考未來的事。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4565
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_990852a9:

    # hi "I suppose that, these days, I've been more concerned with living one day at a time."
    hi "我想，這些日子以來，我比較關心的是過好每一天。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4570
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_f356836e:

    # "Emi considers this for a moment and grins."
    "笑美思索了片刻，然後咧嘴一笑。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4572
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_4c7b6ac1:

    # emi "That's a pretty good idea, Hisao!"
    emi "這是個很棒的想法耶，久夫！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4577
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_98ee7cd9:

    # emi "I just wrote down, 'Pirate.'"
    emi "我直接在職業一欄裡寫入了「海盜」。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4579
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_795b3c15:

    # "I'm momentarily stunned, then I start laughing."
    "我先是愣了一下，然後開始大笑。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4581
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_8d6fd139:

    # "I stop myself and manage to gasp out a question."
    "好不容易控制好自己後，我擠出一個問題："

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4583
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_2c728cf2:

    # hi "You're… you're not actually serious, are you?"
    hi "妳……妳不是認真的吧？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4588
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_970a22ee:

    # "Emi looks mock offended."
    "笑美看上去很受打擊。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4590
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_8aaa1f04:

    # emi "Well I've got the legs for it already, so I just kind of figured…"
    emi "嗯，反正我的腿已經符合標準了，所以我就想說……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4595
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_4f95c161:

    # "Even Rin seems amused by this."
    "就連琳似乎也覺得這很有趣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4600
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_63d0347c:

    # emi "Just you wait, I'll be the terror of the high seas!"
    emi "你們就等著瞧吧，我會成為公海上的恐怖傳說！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4602
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_20b7034d:

    # emi "I'll show you all!"
    emi "我會讓你們刮目相看！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4607
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_4b9981ff:

    # emi "I've even been working on my pirate voice!"
    emi "我甚至還在練習我的海盜腔呢！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4615
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_d2949eef:

    # "She suddenly springs up and begins swaggering up and down the rooftop shouting orders."
    "她突然跳起來，開始在屋頂上大搖大擺地走來走去，大聲下著奇怪的命令。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4620
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_01e605d6:

    # emi "Yarr, me hearties, give 'em a broadside with the long guns!"
    emi "呀兒喲～俺的兄弟們！讓他們嚐嚐咱炮彈的滋味～"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4625
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_24a9888c:

    # emi "We'll wear their guts for garters!"
    emi "把他們的腸子挖出來，當吊帶用！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4630
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_205d2146:

    # rin "Do you even know what that means?"
    rin "妳知道那是什麼意思嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4635
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_effef57a:

    # "Rin's unexpected interruption stops Emi in her tracks."
    "琳出乎意料的打斷讓笑美停下了腳步。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4640
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_8e68a8ae:

    # emi "Not really."
    emi "不太重要。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4645
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_85bb20e0:

    # emi "But it's all in the delivery!"
    emi "重點是氣勢！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4653
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_a37e4a0e:

    # "The ringing of the bell prevents her from demonstrating her point further."
    "鐘聲響起，阻止了她進一步展示她的論點。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4660
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_71f457a3:

    # "Emi dashes off immediately, leaving Rin and myself alone on the roof."
    "笑美立刻衝了出去，留下我和琳獨自在屋頂上。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4670
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_d1ed2d5d:

    # "Rin stares at me intently for a few moments."
    "琳專注地盯著我看了幾秒鐘。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4672
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_bd5814d1:

    # hi "Is there… something wrong?"
    hi "有……什麼事嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4677
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_99fe60c5:

    # "Rin considers this question closely for a moment."
    "琳仔細地思考了這個問題一會兒。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4679
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_26cba132:

    # "After a lengthy pause, she shakes her head."
    "經過一段漫長的停頓後，她搖了搖頭。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4684
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_6a594e55:

    # rin "Nope."
    rin "沒有。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4686
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_c9fbe424:

    # hi "Oh, um…"
    hi "哦，嗯……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4688
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_82f6555c:

    # extend " why the staring, then?"
    extend "那為什麼要盯著我看？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4693
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_fa7aec3f:

    # "Rin shakes her head again."
    "琳又搖了搖她的頭。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4695
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_e0829456:

    # rin "Nope, I don't get it."
    rin "不，我不懂。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4697
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_dad3a1f6:

    # hi "Get what?"
    hi "不懂什麼？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4702
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_786b0a33:

    # rin "The staring thing. You two seem to, but I don't."
    rin "盯著看這件事。你們兩個好像，我不懂。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4704
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_1f720c41:

    # "Great. She saw me staring. Now she probably thinks I'm a pervert or something."
    "太好了。她留意到我盯著笑美看了。現在她可能覺得我是個變態之類的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4706
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_5ad86a37:

    # "Actually, probably not. This is Rin we're talking about, after all."
    "呃，不過話又說回來了，她應該也不會，畢竟這是琳啊。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4708
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_da5ec933:

    # "Still, I feel the need to defend myself."
    "但不管怎樣，我覺得還是有為自己辯解的必要。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4710
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_5913ecd3:

    # hi "I wasn't staring, I was just tired."
    hi "我不是在盯著看，我只是累了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4715
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_76fe2a8f:

    # "Rin actually snorts at this, but she doesn't say anything."
    "琳對此居然哼了一聲，但她什麼也沒說。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4717
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_f10bd427:

    # hi "No, really! I was just… distracted, is all."
    hi "不，真的！我只是……恍神了，就這樣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4722
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_151ce4b7:

    # rin "Mmm."
    rin "嗯…"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4726
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_3f63fd84:

    # "Eager to end this conversation, I head back down to class."
    "我急著結束這段對話，便轉身回教室。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4735
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_6eb76f0d:

    # "I'm greeted by the twin specters of Shizune and Misha, looking like they mean business."
    "我迎面遇上了靜音和米莎這對雙人組，她們看起來一副有公事的樣子。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4737
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_d8db3cb0:

    # "Well, Shizune looks like she means business, anyway."
    "嗯，至少靜音看起來像是有公事。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4739
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_125ea450:

    # "Misha just looks like she's about to start laughing at any minute."
    "米莎則看起來隨時都會笑出來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4746
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_dba189fd:

    # mi "Up on the roof again, Hicchan?"
    mi "又到房頂上面去了嗎，小久？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4751
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_9b7534d8:

    # mi "You know that's dangerous, don't you~?"
    mi "你知道那很危險，對吧～？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4756
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "…"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4761
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_bdd8350f:

    # mi "That's right~!"
    mi "沒錯～！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4766
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_1b11d035:

    # mi "The school cannot be held responsible for any injury that comes from being up there, you know!"
    mi "如果在那裡出了什麼意外，學校可不會負責的哦。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4771
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_c651530e:

    # mi "Furthermore, we could report you for breaking the rules~!"
    mi "而且，我們可以舉報你違反校規喔～！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4776
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_66e0d0de:

    # "Misha leans in and whispers conspiratorially."
    "米莎湊過來，用秘密的口氣小聲地說。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4782
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_ced3d317:

    # mi "But we won't, Hicchan!"
    mi "但我們不會這麼做的啦，小久！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4787
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_09ce4f36:

    # mi "You three are too cute together~!"
    mi "因為你們三個在一起的樣子太可愛了～！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4792
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_4815021d:

    # "She straightens up again, laughing at my sudden blush."
    "她然後直起身子，對著我突然泛紅的臉笑了起來。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4794
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_69277904:

    # mi "Wahahaha~!"
    mi "哇哈哈哈哈～！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4799
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_58c2620f:

    # mi "You're too easy to tease, Hicchan~!"
    mi "你真是太好欺負了，小久～！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4801
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_17c4ca90:

    # hi "Hey, come on."
    hi "喂，別這樣啦。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4803
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_9e8fdf17:

    # hi "I'm still new here, sort of."
    hi "我還算是個新生耶。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4805
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_d5de718e:

    # hi "Isn't it mean to pick on the newcomer like this?"
    hi "這樣欺負新人不是很過分嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4810
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_3f22991d:

    # mi "Nope~!"
    mi "不會～！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4815
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_30cd9e3c:

    # mi "It's to help you get acclimated to your new surroundings!"
    mi "這是為了幫助你適應新環境！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4817
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_6264a5de:

    # hi "Ah, I see."
    hi "啊，我懂了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4819
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_8aad6d60:

    # hi "Well…do you have to be so overzealous about it?"
    hi "嗯……妳們有必要這麼熱心嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4824
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_59065e4c:

    # mi "Yep!"
    mi "對！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4829
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_1e0011dc:

    # mi "Ah! That aside, Hicchan, we were looking for you this morning, but you weren't in your room!"
    mi "啊！先不說那個，小久，我們今天早上都在找你，但你不在你的房間裡！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4831
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_2d60156c:

    # hi "Of course I wasn't. I was out for my morning exercise, or here in class, bright and early."
    hi "我當然不在。我要嘛出去晨跑，要嘛一大早就來教室了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4833
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_f1805f4f:

    # hi "Unlike you."
    hi "跟妳們不一樣。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4839
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_446e6fce:

    # "Shizune looks peeved, and a beat later, so does Misha. Or she tries to, at any rate."
    "靜音看起來挺惱火的，而米莎慢了半拍後也露出了不爽的表情，或至少在試圖這麼做。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4841
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_d876c233:

    # mi "That was because of student council business! You should be grateful that we work so hard for you~!"
    mi "那是因為學生會的事！你應該感謝我們為你們這麼努力工作～！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4843
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_5703ac1d:

    # hi "Oh, I am, I am. So what did you need me for?"
    hi "哦，我很感謝，我很感謝。所以妳們找我有什麼事？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4845
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_01ab5f9b:

    # "Not another attempt to rope me in to do their dirty work, I hope."
    "希望不是又想拉我去做她們的苦工。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4850
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_0d7e57e3:

    # mi "We had to give you something~ but since you weren't around, we dropped it off in your room!"
    mi "我們有東西要給你～但因為你不在，我們就把它放在你房間了！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4852
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_7ca70422:

    # hi "Something? Like what?"
    hi "東西？像是什麼？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4857
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_f5414b3c:

    # mi "Oh, you'll find out when you get back, Hicchan~! Wahahaha~!"
    mi "啊，你回去後就知道了，小久～！啊哈哈哈哈哈～"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4863
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_270b84ab:

    # "Mutou entering the room ends our conversation, and we all head to our seats."
    "武藤老師走進了教室，我們於是結束了談話，返回到各自的座位上。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4867
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_6151a75f:

    # "It's only after I've settled down at my desk and the teacher's started talking about something or other that something odd strikes me."
    "直到我回到座位上，老師開始講話時，我才留意到什麼奇怪的地方。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4869
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_5877251b:

    # "What did Rin mean, 'You two seem to?'"
    "琳說的「你們兩個好像」是什麼意思？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4871
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_1946739c:

    # "Was Emi staring at something too?"
    "難道笑美也在盯著什麼看嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4873
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_28adf005:

    # "For a brief moment, I consider the possibility that Emi was staring at me the way I was staring at her."
    "有那麼一瞬間，我考慮了笑美可能也像我盯著她那樣盯著我。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4875
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_591279b6:

    # "Of course, that's ridiculous."
    "當然，這太離譜了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4877
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_008659bc:

    # "Still, I can't deny that I wouldn't mind if it were true…"
    "不過，我不能否認，如果那是真的，我並不會介意……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4879
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_3a66fb61:

    # "But it's best not to think of that. No need to get my hopes up."
    "但我最好還是別去想。到最後空歡喜一場什麼的沒有必要……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4881
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_219da5b3:

    # "Come to think of it, when did I start having hopes like that anyway?"
    "而話又說回來了，我是什麼時候開始有這種念頭的？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4883
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_c9f751a9:

    # "I shake my head in an attempt to clear it, and focus on the lesson."
    "我使勁搖了搖頭，重新將注意力集中到課堂上。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4888
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_0413476a:

    # "After class, I make my way to my room. Mutou really piled on the homework today."
    "下課後，我回到了我的房間。武藤老師今天真的出了很多作業。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4895
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_3b5e7b11:

    # "Before I can open my door, however, I am suddenly intercepted by Kenji, who has just exploded out of his own room in a flurry of papers."
    "然而，在我開門之前，我突然被健二攔截了，他剛從自己的房間裡衝出來，手上拿著一疊紙。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4897
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_87466949:

    # ke "Hey, we need to talk."
    ke "嘿，我們得談談。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4901
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_7c617827:

    # ke "These rooftop shenanigans of yours, man."
    ke "老兄，你那些在屋頂上的胡鬧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4903
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_1e802382:

    # ke "They've gotta stop."
    ke "必須停止了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4905
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_81d99227:

    # hi "What?"
    hi "什麼？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4907
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_dbbfed1f:

    # ke "Your running around on the rooftop with the limbless wonders!"
    ke "你在屋頂上跟那些缺手缺腳的奇葩鬼混！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4909
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_f87f6230:

    # ke "They're women, man! You'll get yourself killed running around like that!"
    ke "她們是女人啊，哥們！你再那麼做可是會被幹掉的！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4911
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_ed15e901:

    # hi "I don't follow."
    hi "抱歉，我不懂你在說什麼。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4916
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_a3cbb49a:

    # "Kenji sighs and adjusts his glasses, before what could be understood as an attempt at explaining himself patiently."
    "健二嘆了口氣，調整了一下眼鏡，然後用一種可以理解為試圖耐心解釋的態度說話。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4918
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_edf329d4:

    # ke "Look, we're friends so I'm telling you this for your own good."
    ke "聽著，我們是朋友，所以我這是為你好才告訴你。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4920
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_a8f1cbf3:

    # ke "But if I were going to kill someone, I'd do it by throwing them off the roof and making it look like an accident."
    ke "你懂嗎？如果我要殺一個人，我會把他從屋頂上推下去，讓它看起來像個意外。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4925
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_2becd5ea:

    # ke "And if I've thought of it, you can be sure they've thought of it too."
    ke "如果我都想得到，你敢保證她們沒想到嗎？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4927
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_f7102705:

    # ke "They're crafty - almost as crafty as I am."
    ke "她們很狡猾——幾乎跟我一樣狡猾。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4929
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_e1f8a5e6:

    # hi "I see."
    hi "我明白了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4934
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_02a1a8df:

    # ke "Good!"
    ke "很好！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4936
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_0e05690a:

    # ke "I'm glad we had this chat."
    ke "我很高興你能聽進去。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4941
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_eeadf269:

    # ke "Loan me 500 yen."
    ke "借我五百圓。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4943
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_2dfb8f13:

    # hi "…I'm sorry?"
    hi "……你說什麼？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4948
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_e9e98be1:

    # ke "I need to get a drink, man!"
    ke "我需要去買點喝的，老兄！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4950
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_cc0e8c2e:

    # ke "I've been inside all day and the tap water's been compromised, as I'm sure you know."
    ke "我一整天都沒出去。自來水已經被污染了，我相信你知道的。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4952
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_f52b51fd:

    # ke "So I need to stock up on something canned, got it? But to do that, I need 500 yen."
    ke "所以我需要囤積一些罐裝的東西，懂嗎？所以，我需要五百圓。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4957
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_90ea7f01:

    # ke "And since I've just saved your life with my timely advice, you can at least spare me 500 yen."
    ke "既然我剛用我及時的建議救了你一命，你至少可以借我五百圓吧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4959
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_c242e84e:

    # "You know, if it'll make him go away, 500 yen is a bargain."
    "你知道嗎，如果能讓他走開，五百圓算是很划算了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4969
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_521270a7:

    # "I hand the money over to Kenji, who nods in thanks and dashes off down the hallway, but not before he locks his door."
    "我把錢給健二，他點頭道謝後衝下走廊，當然，在那之前，他鎖上了他的門。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4971
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_ef6cd37e:

    # "What an exhausting person. I'd better go, in case he changes his mind."
    "真是個累人的傢伙。我最好趕快進去，免得他又改變主意。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4976
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_00ea3b67:

    # "Hm?"
    "嗯？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4978
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_6dd40b9b:

    # "As I close the door, my heel taps against something lying on the floor."
    "當我關上門時，我的腳跟碰到了地板上的某樣東西。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4980
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_c3406a0c:

    # "It's a brightly-colored rectangle of paper. Ah, this must be the 'something' Misha mentioned before."
    "那是一張色彩鮮豔的長方形紙片。啊，這一定就是米莎之前提到的「東西」。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4982
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_55658247:

    # "Probably a student council leaflet she slid under the door."
    "大概是她從門縫下塞進來的學生會傳單吧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4984
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_f086bf97:

    # "However, when I pick it up, I find that I couldn't have been more wrong."
    "然而，當我撿起來時，才發現我錯得離譜。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4986
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_8615a4ad:

    # "Someone actually wrote me an old-fashioned, hand-written paper letter."
    "居然有人寄給我一封老式的、手寫的信。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4988
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_f4dab597:

    # "Who bothers doing something like that in this day and age, anyway? Yet, as unlikely as the prospect of receiving one sounds, this is definitely a letter I have in my hands."
    "都什麼年代了，誰還會費心做這種事啊？然而，儘管收到一封信聽起來多麼不可思議，我手上確確實實是一封信。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4990
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_0c7518bc:

    # "I was planning on finishing my homework, getting some dinner, and going to bed in order to be ready for tomorrow morning's run."
    "我本來打算寫完作業，吃點晚餐，然後上床睡覺，為明早的晨跑做準備。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4992
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_78ea0144:

    # "However, the letter has naturally caught my interest. I sit at my desk to examine it properly."
    "然而，這封信自然引起了我的興趣。我坐在書桌前，仔細地檢視它。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5001
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_d21c5bd8:

    # "It's the first piece of mail I've received here at Yamaku, so it'd feel special even if it wasn't something as rare as a handwritten letter."
    "這是我在山久收到的第一封信，所以即使它不是手寫信這麼稀有的東西，也很特別。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5003
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_2beb101c:

    # "What causes me even more trepidation is the name of the sender, written neatly on the back of the envelope."
    "更讓我訝異的是寄件人的名字。整齊地寫在信封的背面。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5005
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_a9c40d09:

    # "'Iwanako.'"
    "「巖魚子。」"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5007
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_799ef6f3:

    # "I have no idea why she would write to me. I haven't been in contact with anyone from my old school since I transferred, and Iwanako is the last person I'd expect to want to write me a letter."
    "我完全不知道她為什麼會寫信給我。自從我轉學後，我就沒跟我以前學校的任何人聯絡了，而巖魚子是我最想不到會寫信給我的人。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5011
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5014
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_f94e2c99:

    # n "{vspace=150}The last time I saw Iwanako was terribly awkward; embarrassingly so. She came to my hospital room, peeled me an apple out of courtesy and then we practically sat in silence for half an hour."
    n "{vspace=150}我最後一次見到巖魚子時非常尷尬；尷尬到令人難堪。她來到我的病房，出於禮貌幫我削了個蘋果，然後我們幾乎沉默地坐了半個小時。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5016
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_a36a2027:

    # n "She said 'goodbye' and didn't look me in the eye when she closed the door."
    n "她說了「再見」，關上門時沒有看我的眼睛。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5018
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_0051aa8c:

    # n "It might've been a natural end to the series of visits that were probably pretty painful for both of us."
    n "那或許是一個自然的結束。在對我們倆都相當痛苦的一系列探病之後。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5020
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_0e1eccb2:

    # n "Every time she visited me in the hospital I wanted to talk to her, but something stopped me every time."
    n "每次她在醫院探望我時，我都想跟她說話，但每次都有什麼東西阻止了我。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5022
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_3e5f58b5:

    # n "Every time that I didn't speak made the next time even harder."
    n "每一次的沉默都讓下一次開口變得更加困難。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5024
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_b4ee1ed1:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=120}She looked so guilty that I didn't want to say anything that might upset her, and I never could figure out the right words to say."
    nvl clear
    n "{vspace=120}她看起來那麼內疚，我不想說任何可能讓她難過的話，而且我始終想不出該說些什麼才好。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5028
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_d3fbad16:

    # n "I think Iwanako blamed herself for my heart attack. That's ridiculous, of course, but knowing it and believing it are two very different things."
    n "我想巖魚子一定把我的心臟病發作歸咎於她自己。當然，這很荒謬，但知道和相信畢竟是兩回事。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5030
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_7f8abf22:

    # n "I told her that it wasn't her fault, she nodded and I really think she understood that if it hadn't been that, then sooner or later something else would've made my heart give out."
    n "我跟她說那不是她的錯，她點了點頭。我想她知道即便那種事情沒有發生，遲早我的心臟也會以另外的、更為戲劇化的方式使我崩潰"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5032
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_ade77ce8:

    # n "Yet she looked so hopelessly sad every time she opened that door and entered my room."
    n "但她每次進入我的病房時看上去都那麼的痛苦、那麼的無助。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5034
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_c8fc7c4a:

    # n "So I never managed to say the things I wanted to say. In the end, that might've hurt her even more."
    n "所以我始終沒能說出我想說的話。到頭來，那或許傷她更深。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5039
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_76b2fe88_2:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5044
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_ad45b62a:

    # "Carefully, I open the envelope and draw out the folded letter from within."
    "我小心翼翼地打開信封，從裡面抽出折疊好的信紙。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5056
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_c4d0fca6:

    # "Yeah, I think I have had quite enough of this."
    "是啊，我想我已經受夠了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5061
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_9049c309:

    # "I crumple up the sheet of paper and toss it across the room. My aim is off, so the letter rolls under my nightstand instead of going into my wastebasket."
    "我把信紙揉成一團，扔到房間的另一頭。我沒丟準，紙團滾到了我的床頭櫃底下，而不是我的垃圾桶裡。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5063
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_be3de3e0:

    # "That was an apology for abandoning me. Except I don't know that I really need it any more, at this point."
    "那是一封為拋棄我而寫的道歉信。只是事到如今，我不知道我是否還真的需要它。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5065
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_b07c4d50:

    # "The hospital seems like a lifetime ago, and here, now, I've got other things on my mind."
    "醫院的日子感覺像上輩子的事了，而此時此地，我有其他事情要煩心。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5069
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_a2492405:

    # "Emi, for starters."
    "首先，是笑美。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5071
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_f012923b:

    # "It wasn't great to be abandoned during my stay, but it's not something I'm worried about any more."
    "住院期間被拋下感覺很糟，但我已經不在意了。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5073
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_543ed83e:

    # "In fact, I hadn't even thought about the hospital in what feels like forever until this letter came in. It's almost annoying to have received it."
    "事實上，看到這封信之前，我已經很久沒想到過醫院的事了。收到這封信反而讓人覺得煩躁。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5075
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_49580b70:

    # "I've got exams to study for, myself. I have no time for the past."
    "我還有考試要準備，沒時間去理會過去。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5077
translate zh_hant a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_ae576d7f:

    # "Now, about that homework…"
    "好了，開始寫作業吧。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5090
translate zh_hant a2_emi_famous_last_words_b8f57914:

    # hi "So what's the plan for today anyway?"
    hi "那麼今天的計劃到底是什麼？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5097
translate zh_hant a2_emi_famous_last_words_c98c7103:

    # "I'm waiting patiently in the hallway of the girls' dormitory just outside of Emi and Rin's rooms."
    "我正在女生宿舍的走廊上耐心等待。就在笑美和琳的房門外。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5099
translate zh_hant a2_emi_famous_last_words_f3c77901:

    # "Emi is apparently helping Rin with getting dressed."
    "笑美顯然正在幫琳穿衣服。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5101
translate zh_hant a2_emi_famous_last_words_fade2441:

    # "I suppose that makes perfect sense, as I've no idea how Rin would get dressed otherwise."
    "這完全合情合理，因為我實在不知道琳自己要怎麼穿衣服。"

